\id 1CO
\h 1 Ikurintiyyen 
\toc1 1 Ikurintiyyen 
\toc2 1 Ikurintiyyen 
\toc3 1 Kur. 
\mt1 1 Ikurintiyyen  
\c 1
\s1 Aseǧem ɣar umezwaru  
\m
\v 1 Bulus, \add rrasul\add* ittwařaɣan d ittwasekken n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ɛlaḥsab min ixs AREBBI, d tawmat Sustinis, \f ◼ \fr 1:1 \ft \+fk rrasul\ft  - niɣ ‘amazan’.\f*  
\v 2 i tmesmunt n AREBBI i iǧan di Kurintus, inni ittwařaɣan d inni d imqeddasen, inni ittwaqeddsen di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, u i marra inni mani ma ittřaɣan x Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, wenni d Siditsen d Siditneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Yḥ. 17:19; Řex. 15:9; Rum. 1:7; Afa. 1:1; 1 Ts. 4:7; 2 Tim. 2:22. \x*  
\v 3 Ad xawem yiři arḍa d řehna zi AREBBI, Babatneɣ, u zi Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Rum. 1:7; 2 Kur. 1:2; Afa. 1:2; 1 Bṭ. 1:2. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Necc řebda ttqadiɣ AREBBI inu di ṭṭweɛ nwem x arḍa n AREBBI i d awem immewcen di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.  
\v 5 Minzi di marra tdewřem zzayes d ttujjar, di marra awař u di marra tussna, \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Kul. 1:9. \x*  
\v 6 maɣar cchadet n Lmasiḥ tᵉttwaḍmen daywem,  
\v 7 minzi uřa d ijj n zzɛaf n tewhibin nnes war daywem iqqim, \add am\add* tᵉttrajam asargab n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Fil. 3:20; Tit. 2:13. \x*  
\v 8 Minzi Netta ad kenniw iḍmen ɛawed ɣar uneggar, ḥima ad tiřim břa řɛib deg wass n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt 1 Ts. 3:13; 5:23. \x*  
\v 9 AREBBI d amtiqqi, d wenni zi tᵉttwařaɣam kenniw ɣar tmunt ak-d Mmis Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, Siditneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Irm. 32:40-44; Yḥ. 15:5; 1 Kur. 10:13; Gal. 2:20; 1 Ts. 5:24; 1 Yḥ. 1:3. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ařaɣi ɣar umuni d ijjen di Lmasiḥ  
\m
\v 10 Maca ttzawageɣ kenniw, \add a\add* aytma, s Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, ad tessiwřem marra s ijj n wawař, war tᵉttemsebḍim jar awem, maca iřim tmunem nican s nneyyet d icten d uxarreṣ d ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Rum. 12:16; 15:5; Fil. 2:2; 3:16; 1 Bṭ. 3:8. \x*  
\v 11 Minzi ssargben ayi inni zi taddart n Kluwi, \add a\add* aytma inu, belli jar awem imenɣan.  
\v 12 Xseɣ ad iniɣ, aqa ca zzaywem qqaren: ‘Necc aqa ayi zi Bulus!’ u ca nneɣni: ‘Necc zi Apullus!’, u ca nneɣni \add ɛawed\add*: ‘Necc zi Kifa!’, u ca nneɣni qqaren: ‘Necc zi Lmasiḥ!’ \x ◘ \xo 1:12 \xt Řex. 18:24; 1 Kur. 3:4; 16:12. \x*  
\v 13 Ma aqa Lmasiḥ ittwabḍa \add d iwetwiten\add*? Ma tuɣa Bulus ittwaṣelleb di ssibbet nwem? Niɣ tuɣa kenniw tᵉttwassɣeḍṣem s yisem n Bulus?  
\v 14 Necc ttqadiɣ AREBBI inu war ssɣeḍṣeɣ uřa d ijj zzaywem mɣir Krispus d Xayus waha, \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Řex. 18:8; Rum. 16:23. \x*  
\v 15 ařami uřa d ijjen ad yini belli ssɣeḍṣeɣ deg yisem inu.  
\v 16 Ɛawed ssɣeḍṣeɣ tawacunt n Stifanus, xenni war ssineɣ ca, ma ssɣeḍṣeɣ ḥed nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Kur. 16:15, 17. \x*  
\v 17 Maɣar Lmasiḥ war d ayi dd-issekk ḥima ad ssɣeḍṣeɣ, maca ḥima ad barrḥeɣ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan, war iǧi s tiɣit n wawařen, ḥima war ittᵉttwassbeṭṭeř ṣṣalib n Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt 1 Kur. 2:1, 4; 2 Bṭ. 1:16. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tiɣit n Arebbi  
\m
\v 18 Minzi awař n ṣṣalib d tubbuheřya di tiṭṭawin n yinni i ɣa iweddaren, maca i neccin, inni iddaren, man aya d jjehd n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt Rum. 1:16. \x*  
\v 19 Minzi tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ad areddǧeɣ tiɣit n imiɣisen\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad kkseɣ řefhamet n ifehhamen.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:19 \xt Ayub 5:12; Ica. 29:14. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Mani iǧa umiɣis? Mani iǧa umseřmad n idlisen? Mani iǧa bu-umḥarweḍ n ddunect-a? Ma war isscen AREBBI belli tiɣit n ddunect-a d tubbuheřya? \x ◘ \xo 1:20 \xt Ica. 33:18. \x*  
\v 21 Minzi di tiɣit n AREBBI, ddunect war tessin ca AREBBI zi ssibbet n tiɣit \add n yixef nnes\add*, aqa tuɣa yarḍa AREBBI ad iwc Tudart i yinni yumnen s tubbuheřya n tbarreḥt. \x ◘ \xo 1:21 \xt Mt. 11:25; Lk. 10:21. \x*  
\v 22 Minzi Udayen ttaren řeɛřamat u Iramiyyen arezzun tiɣit, \x ◘ \xo 1:22 \xt Mt. 12:38; 16:1; Yḥ. 4:48. \x*  
\v 23 maca neccin nettbarreḥ Lmasiḥ, d wenni ittwaṣellben, aqa-t d taɛenkrift i Wudayen, d tubbuheřya i Iramiyyen, \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt Mt. 11:6. Yḥ. 6:60, 66. \x*  
\v 24 maca i yinni ittwařaɣan, am Wudayen am Iramiyyen, aqa Lmasiḥ d jjehd n AREBBI d tiɣit n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 1:24 \xt Kul. 2:3. \x*  
\v 25 Minzi tubbuheřya n AREBBI d tmiɣist x iwdan, u tuḍɛeft n AREBBI tejhed x iwdan.   
\m
\v 26 Xenni, \add a\add* aytma, xzarem \add mammec teǧam\add* ɣar \add wass n\add* třaɣit nwem, aqa war teǧim d aṭṭas n imiɣisen ɛlaḥsab bnadem, niɣ d aṭṭas n yinni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa, niɣ d aṭṭas n tarwa n taṣiřet. \x ◘ \xo 1:26 \xt Yḥ. 7:48; Yaɛ. 2:5. \x*  
\v 27 Maɣar AREBBI aqa ifarz ibuhařiyyen n ddunect, ḥima ad zzaysen isseḥcem imiɣisen, uca imuḍɛifen n ddunect ifarz i-ten AREBBI, ḥima ad zzaysen isseḥcem ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa.  
\v 28 uca yinni dd-ixeřqen am war ɣarsen ca di ddunect, d yinni ittwasseḥqaren, d yinni war iǧin d ca, aqa ifarz i-ten AREBBI, ḥima ad ibḍeř inni iǧan d ca,  
\v 29 ḥima uřa d ijj n \add bnadem n\add* weysum, war ittfeyyec ca zzates.  
\v 30 Maca kenniw teǧam zzayes di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, wenni d aneɣ idewřen d tiɣit n AREBBI d tsegda d tuqeddsi d usenjem, \x ◘ \xo 1:30 \xt Irm. 23:5; Yḥ. 17:19. \x*  
\v 31 am mammec tura: \qt “Ejj wenni issemɣaran, ad issemɣar di SIDI.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:31 \xt Ica. 65:16; Irm. 9:22-23; 2 Kur. 10:17. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Ṣṣifet n tsexxart n Bulus  
\m
\v 1 \add A\add* aytma, řami dd-usiɣ ɣarwem, war dd-usiɣ ca ḥima ad awem barrḥeɣ Řexbar Aṣebḥan n ssirr n AREBBI s tbezzaḥt n wawař niɣ s tiɣit, \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt 1 Kur. 1:17; 2:4. \x*  
\v 2 minzi aqa tuɣa ɛewwřeɣ ḥima war ttessneɣ ca jar awem mɣir Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, d Wenni ittwaṣellben ɛawed.  
\v 3 Tuɣa ayi akidwem s waṭṭas n tiggʷudi d uqdides. \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Řex. 18:1, 3; 2 Kur. 10:10. \x*  
\v 4 Tabrat inu d tbarreḥt inu war dd-usint-i-dd s wawařen izewwqen n tiɣit \add n bnadem\add*, maca s wescan n Arruḥ d jjehd, \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt 1 Kur. 1:17; 2:1; 2 Bṭ. 1:16. \x*  
\v 5 ḥima l’iman nwem war ittbeddi ca x tiɣit n iwdan, maca x jjehd n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt 2 Kur. 4:7. \x*   
\m
\v 6 Maca nessawař s tiɣit i yinni t iwḍen, aqa s ict n tiɣit tenni war iǧin n ddunect-a niɣ n řḥukkam n ddunect-a, inni i ɣa ittwassbeṭṭřen, \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Ayub 28:21; 1 Kur. 15:24. \x*  
\v 7 maca nessawař tiɣit n AREBBI s ijj n ssirr i tuɣa inuffaren, wenni tuɣa izzar ifarz i-t AREBBI i uɛuǧi nneɣ qbeř i tuɣa din zzmanat. \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt Rum. 16:25; 1 Kur. 4:1. \x*  
\v 8 \add Wa d ssirr\add* nni war t issin uřa d ijj zi řḥukkam n ddunect-a, minzi mařa tuɣa ssnen t, iři war ṣellben ɛemmarṣ Sidi n uɛuǧi. \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt Mt. 11:25; Yḥ. 7:48; 16:3; Řex. 3:17; 13:27; 2 Kur. 3:14; 1 Tim. 1:13. \x*  
\v 9 Maca am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Min war teẓri tiṭṭ d min war isři umezzuɣ\qt*  
\m \qt d min war yudifen ca ɣar wuř n bnadem,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa man aya issewjed i-t AREBBI i yinni t ittexsen.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:9 \xt Ica. 64:3. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 Maca AREBBI immeř aneɣ t s Arruḥ nnes, minzi Arruḥ tarezzu kuřci uřa d řaǧaɣ n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 2:10 \xt Mt. 13:11; 2 Kur. 3:18. \x*  
\v 11 Minzi man wen d bnadem i issnen min iǧan di bnadem mɣir arruḥ n bnadem wenni dayes iǧan. Ammu ɛawed uřa d ijj war issin ca min iǧan di AREBBI mɣir Arruḥ n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Awřn. 27:19; Irm. 17:9. \x*   
\m
\v 12 Aqa neccin war neksi ca arruḥ n ddunect, maca Arruḥ i dd-yusin zi AREBBI, ḥima ad nessen min d aneɣ iwca AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Rum. 8:15. \x*  
\v 13 S uyenni awařen i zi nessawař, war ǧin d tɣuri s wawařen n tiɣit n bnadem, maca d tɣuri zi Arruḥ, ḥima ad nessemqudda min iǧan n arruḥ ak-d min iǧan n arruḥ. \x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt 1 Kur. 1:17; 2:4; 2 Bṭ. 1:16\x*  
\v 14 Maɣar bnadem s yixef nnes war iqebbeř ca min iǧan n Arruḥ, minzi iḥesb i-t d tubbuheřya, war izemmar ad t ifhem, minzi man aya izemmar ad ittwafarz s Arruḥ waha.  
\v 15 Maca bnadem arruḥani aqa izemmar ad ifarz kuřci, maca netta simant nnes war xas iḥekkem uřa d ijj. \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Awřn. 28:5. \x*  
\v 16 Minzi wi issnen axemmem n SIDI ařami \add izemmar\add* ad t isseřmed? Maca neccin ɣarneɣ axemmem n Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 2:16 \xt Ica. 40:13; Rum. 11:34. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Řebni n l’iman x dsas nican  
\m
\v 1 \add A\add* aytma, necc war zemmareɣ ad kiwem ssiwřeɣ am iwdan inni iddaren ɛlaḥsab Arruḥ, maca am yinni iddaren ɛlaḥsab aysum \add n bnadem\add* waha, amecnaw iseyman di Lmasiḥ.  
\v 2 Aqa wciɣ awem ad teswem aɣi, war iǧi d ařeqqim imten, minzi tuɣa war d as tzemmarem, ař i řexxu u war d as tzemmarem ɛad, \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Ɛbr. 5:12; 1 Bṭ. 2:2. \x*  
\v 3 s minzi kenniw ɛad deg weysum. Maɣar mařa din \add ɛad\add* jar awem řeḥsed d imenɣan d umsebḍi, ma war teǧim ɛad n ddat niɣ teggurem \add ɛad\add* deg weysum? \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt 1 Kur. 1:11; Gal. 5:19; Yaɛ. 3:16. \x*  
\v 4 Minzi mařa ijjen zzaywem iqqar: ‘Necc aqa ayi zi Bulus!’ u wenneɣni iqqar: ‘Necc aqa ayi zi Apullus!’, ma xenni kenniw war teǧim ca ddat? \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt 1 Kur. 1:12. \x*  
\v 5 Maɣar min iɛna Apullus u min iɛna Bulus? Aqa aten mɣir d imsexxaren i zi tdewřem tumnem, uca kuř ijjen am mammec d as iwca SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Řex. 18:24; 1 Kur. 1:12; 16:12. \x*  
\v 6 Aqa necc ẓẓuɣ, Apullus issu, maca AREBBI isseɣmi. \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Řex. 18:26; 19:1. \x*  
\v 7 Xenni wenni itteẓẓun war iǧi d ca uřa d wenni ittessun, maca AREBBI wenni issɣemmayen.  
\v 8 Maca wenni itteẓẓun d wenni ittessun d ijjen, waxxa kuř ijj tekkar as-dd řmunet nnes am mammec řxedmet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:8 \xt Izhd. 62:13; Irm. 17:10; 32:19; Mt. 16:27; Rum. 2:6; 14:12; 2 Kur. 5:10; Gal. 6:5; Asa. 2:23; 22:12. \x*  
\v 9 Minzi neccin d imsexxaren ak-d AREBBI uca kenniw d tafeǧaḥt d řebni n AREBBI i teǧam. \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt 2 Kur. 6:1; Afa. 2:20; Kul. 2:7; 1 Bṭ. 2:5. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Ɛlaḥsab arḍa n AREBBI i d ayi immewcen, necc, am řemɛeǧem abennay amiɣis, ggiɣ dsas u wenneɣni ad xas ibna. Ejj kuř ijj ad iḥḍa mammec xas i ɣa ibna.  
\v 11 Minzi uřa d ijjen war izemmar ad igg dsas nneɣni x wenni immarsen, aqa-t d Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt Ica. 28:16; Mt. 16:18. \x*  
\v 12 Uca mařa ibna ḥed x dsas nni s wureɣ, nnuqart, iẓra iɣřan, tefřawt. řum niɣ s uxecxuc,  
\v 13 řxedmet n kuř ijjen ad tban, minzi ass ad tt isscen. Minzi s timessi ad ittwasseḍhar mammec teǧa řxedmet n kuř ijj, timessi ad tt tfarz. \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Ica. 8:20; 48:10; Irm. 23:29; 1 Bṭ. 1:7; 4:12. \x*  
\v 14 Mařa teqqim řxedmet \add n řebni\add* i \add xas\add* tuɣa ibna ca n ijjen, aqa netta ad iṭṭef řmunet nnes,  
\v 15 u mařa tecmeḍ řxedmet n ca n ijjen, aqa netta ad yarbu taxessart nnes, maca netta simant nnes ad injem axmi ikka timessi.   
\m
\v 16 Ma war tessinem ca belli teǧam d zzawect n AREBBI uca belli Arruḥ n AREBBI izeddeɣ daywem? \x ◘ \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Kur. 6:19; 2 Kur. 6:16; Ɛbr. 3:6; 1 Bṭ. 2:5. \x*  
\v 17 Mařa yareyyeb ḥed zzawect n AREBBI, AREBBI ad t yareyyeb, minzi zzawect n AREBBI, tenni teǧam kenniw, tqeddes i teǧa.   
\m
\v 18 War ttejji ḥed ad ixeddeɛ ixef nnes! Mařa din ḥed jar awem ittɣiř as ixef nnes d amiɣis di ddunect-a, ejj i-t ad idweř d abuhaři maḥend ad yiři d amiɣis. \x ◘ \xo 3:18 \xt Awřn. 3:7; Ica. 5:21. \x*  
\v 19 Minzi tiɣit n ddunect-a teǧa d tubbuheřya ɣar AREBBI, minzi tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Iṭṭef imiɣisen s teḥraymect nsen!”,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:19 \xt Ayub 5:13. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 uca ɛawed:  
\b  
\m \qt “SIDI issnen aqa ixarriṣen n imiɣisen d řbaṭeř.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:20 \xt Izhd. 94:11. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 21 S uya, uřa d ijjen war issemɣari ca zeg iwdan, minzi marra nwem,  
\v 22 ma d Bulus, niɣ d Apullus, niɣ d Kifa, niɣ d ddunect, niɣ d tudart, niɣ d řmewt, niɣ d iḍa niɣ d tiwecca, aqa marra nwem,  
\v 23 maca kenniw n Lmasiḥ uca Lmasiḥ n AREBBI.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Rrusul n Lmasiḥ  
\m
\v 1 Ejj aneɣ xenni ad nettwaḥseb zzaywem am imsexxaren n Lmasiḥ u am iwkiřen n řesrar n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Mt. 24:45; 2 Kur. 6:4; Kul. 1:25; Tit. 1:7. \x*  
\v 2 Xenni ittxeṣṣa i mkuř awkiř ad ittwaf d amtiqqi. \x ◘ \xo 4:2 \xt Lk. 12:42. \x*  
\v 3 Necc war d ayi icqi ca mařa ttwaḥekmeɣ zzaywem niɣ zeg ijj n bnadem \add nneɣni\add*. Uřa d necc war ḥekkmeɣ ca x ixef inu.  
\v 4 Minzi necc war uciɣ s ca \add war iḥřin\add* dayi, maca s man aya war ttwaseggdeɣ, maɣar aqa SIDI d Řqaḍi inu. \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt Uf. 34:7; Ayub 9:2; Izhd. 143:2. \x*  
\v 5 S uyenni war ḥekkmem ca x walu qbeř řweqt nni di dd ɣa yas SIDI, wenni i ɣa issuffɣen ɣar tfawt min innufaren di taǧest, wenni i ɣa isseḍharen ixarriṣen n wuřawen. Uca řexdenni kuř ijj ad ɣares yiři usemɣar zi AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 4:5 \xt Dan. 7:10; Mt. 7:1; Rum. 2:1; Asa. 20:12. \x*   
\m
\v 6 Aqa man aya, \add a\add* aytma, iwyeɣ t-i-dd xafi u x Apullus am yijj n umedya di ṭṭweɛ nwem, ḥima ad zzayneɣ třemdem, maḥend war tᵉttxarriṣem ca barra i min iǧan di tira, ḥima uřa d ijj ad issemɣar ixef nnes ḍidd i wenni d as yudsen di ssibbet n yijjen nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt Awřn. 3:7; Rum. 12:3. \x*  
\v 7 Man wen yarezzun dayek? Niɣ min ɣarek nni war tᵉṭṭifed? Uca mařa tᵉṭṭfed t, mayemmi tcennɛed axmi war t tᵉṭṭifed ca? \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Yḥ. 3:27; Yaɛ. 1:17. \x*  
\v 8 Řexxu aqa tejjiwnem u tdewřem tᵉttejjarem, uca břa neccin aqa tḥekkmem \add am ijeǧiden\add*. Meɛlik kenniw tḥekkmem \add am ijeǧiden\add*, ad yiři neccin xenni ad neḥkem ɛawed akidwem!  
\v 9 Minzi ittɣiř ayi belli AREBBI igga aneɣ ɣar uneggar, neccin inni iǧan d rrusul, axmi \add xaneɣ ḥekmen s\add* řmewt, minzi aqa nedweř d afurrej i ddunect, i lmalakat u i iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Izhd. 44:23; Rum. 8:36; 2 Kur. 4:11; Ɛbr. 10:33. \x*  
\v 10 Neccin neǧa d ibuhařiyyen x ssibbet n Lmasiḥ, maca kenniw teǧam d imiɣisen di Lmasiḥ. Neccin nheyyef, kenniw tjehdem, kenniw tᵉttwacennɛem, neccin nettwasseḥqara. \x ◘ \xo 4:10 \xt 1 Kur. 2:3. \x*  
\v 11 Ař řexxu neccin dayney řaẓ d ufadi d tuɛaryent, ccaten aneɣ, war ɣarneɣ bu tzeddiɣt, \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Řex. 23:2. \x*  
\v 12 narebber am nxeddem s ifassen nneɣ. Nitni sseḥqaran aneɣ, aqa aneɣ ad nbarek, darrcen xaneɣ, maca aqa nkessi armeḥ, \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Mt. 5:44; Lk. 6:28; 23:34; Řex. 7:60; 18:3; 20:34; Rum. 12:14; 1 Ts. 2:9; 2 Ts. 3:8. \x*  
\v 13 ceqqfen dayneɣ, aqa nettḥeccem i-ten \add di řxir\add*. Ař řexxu nedweř am tzubač n ddunect, am ifuraḍ n marra, ař i řexxu.   
\m
\v 14 War ttariɣ aya ḥima ad kenniw sseḥcimeɣ, maca ttziyyareɣ kenniw am tarwa iɛizzen. \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt 1 Ts. 2:11. \x*  
\v 15 Waxxa mařa tuɣa din ɣarwem ɛecra-ařaf n yinni i kenniw yarebban di Lmasiḥ, aqa war ɣarwem aṭṭas n ibabaten, minzi necc jjiɣ-dd kenniw di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ s L’Injil. \x ◘ \xo 4:15 \xt Řex. 18:11; Gal. 4:19; Flmn. 10; Yaɛ. 1:18. \x*  
\v 16 S uyenni ttarreɣ zzaywem: Arewsem ayi! \x ◘ \xo 4:16 \xt 1 Kur. 11:1; Fil. 3:17; 1 Ts. 1:6; 2 Ts. 3:9. \x*  
\v 17 S uyenni ssekkeɣ awem-dd Timutiyu, wenni iǧan d mmi iɛizzen d amtiqqi di SIDI, ḥima ad d awem issfekkar ibriden inu i iǧan di Lmasiḥ, am mammec ten sseřmadeɣ di marra timesmunin.   
\m
\v 18 Maca ca zzaywem aqa ttneffaxen, axmi necc war ɣarwem ttiwiḍiɣ.  
\v 19 Maca mařa ixs SIDI ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ deɣya. Xenni war ttexseɣ \add zeɛma\add* ad ssneɣ awařen n yinni issgeɛɛden ixef nsen, maca jjehd nsen. \x ◘ \xo 4:19 \xt Řex. 18:21; Ɛbr. 6:3; Yaɛ. 4:15. \x*  
\v 20 Minzi Tageldit n AREBBI war teǧi ca deg wawař\add en\add*, maca di jjehd. \x ◘ \xo 4:20 \xt 1 Kur. 2:4; 1 Ts. 1:5; 2 Bṭ. 1:16. \x*  
\v 21 Min texsem? Ma ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ s weɛmud niɣ s tayri u s arruḥ n temhint?   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Asḥeyyed n ijj n umednub zi tmesmunt  
\m
\v 1 Řḥasuř, ittwanna belli aqa din jar awem farq-ccɣeř, u anect n farq-ccɣeř nni war iǧin qaɛ jar lkuffar, aqa ijj n mmis ɣares tamɣart n babas. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt Lawi 18:8; Aɛwd. 27:20. \x*  
\v 2 Kenniw tessuffam ixef nwem, waxxa ittxeṣṣa awem di tidett ad tceḍnem, ḥima ad tḥeyyḍem wenni iggin man aya zi řwesṭ nwem.  
\v 3 Waxxa necc aggʷejeɣ ɛlaḥsab arrimet, aqa ayi ḥḍareɣ di Arruḥ, uca aqa ḥekmeɣ axmi ḥḍareɣ x wenni iggin man aya.  
\v 4 Ittxeṣṣa ad tmunem marra deg Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, u necc akidwem di Arruḥ, s jjehd n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ,  
\v 5 uca kenniw ad t tsellmem i cciṭan i txessart n arrimet nnes, ḥima ad iddar di Arruḥ deg wass n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt 1 Tim. 1:20. \x*   
\m
\v 6 War dd xawem yusi ufeyyec! Ma war tessinem ca belli cwayt n wentun issmemm marra taɛebbuzt n warecti? \x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt Gal. 5:9. \x*  
\v 7 Sizedgem ixef nwem xenni zeg wentun aqdim, ḥima ad tiřim d ict n řɛejnet n warecti n jdid. Aqa kenniw d aɣrum břa antun, minzi \add Taɣarṣt nneɣ n\add* Useɛdu aqa tᵉttwaɣarṣ i neccin, aqa \add Netta\add* d Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 5:7 \xt Ica. 53:7; Yḥ. 1:29; 1 Kur. 15:3. \x*  
\v 8 S uyenni ejj aneɣ ad nɛeyyed, war iǧi s wentun aqdim niɣ s wentun n tuɛeffna d řɣar, maca s wentun n řeṣfayet d tqeddast. \x ◘ \xo 5:8 \xt Uf. 12:3, 15; Aɛwd. 16:3. \x*   
\m
\v 9 Aqa uriɣ awem-dd di tebrat, ittxeṣṣa war ttɛacarem ayt n farq-ccɣeř \x ◘ \xo 5:9 \xt Aɛwd. 7:2; Mt. 18:17; 2 Kur. 6:14; Afa. 5:11; 2 Ts. 3:14. \x*  
\v 10 War ssiwřeɣ x ayt n farq-ccɣeř nni iǧan di ddunect-a, niɣ x iḍemmaɛen niɣ x ibeɛɛaj niɣ x yinni iɛebbden l’aṣnam, mařa ammu, iři ad teffɣem zi ddunect-a.  
\v 11 Maca uriɣ awem-dd řexxu, ḥima war tᵉttɛacarem ca ḥed, waxxa qqaren as uma, maca aqa-t d bu-farq-ccɣeř, niɣ d aḍemmaɛ, niɣ d wenni iɛebbden l’aṣnam, niɣ d amceqqaf, niɣ d askarji, niɣ d aceffar. Ak-d ḥed am wanita war kis tᵉttettem \add ɛad\add* aɣrum! \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Řxř. 12:14; Mt. 18:17; 2 Ts. 3:14; 2 Yḥ. 10. \x*  
\v 12 Minzi man řḥeqq ɣari, ḥima ad ḥekmeɣ x yinni iǧan barra? Ḥekkmem kenniw x yinni iǧan daxeř!  
\v 13 Maca inni iǧan barra, AREBBI ad xasen iḥkem. Sḥeyydem xawem aɛeffan! \x ◘ \xo 5:13 \xt Aɛwd. 17:7\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Imcubbac jar wawmaten  
\m
\v 1 Ma izɛem ḥed zzaywem, xmi ɣares ccreɛ ak-d wenneɣni, ad \add zzayes\add* iḥkem zzat n yinni war iseggden, war iǧi zzat i imqeddasen?  
\v 2 Niɣ war tessinem ca belli imqeddasen ad ḥekmen ddunect? Uca mařa \add xenni\add* ddunect ad tᵉttwaḥkem zzaywem, ma war tzemmarem \add xenni\add* ad tɛedřem ddɛawi timeẓyanin \add jar awem\add*? \x ◘ \xo 6:2 \xt Mt. 19:28; Lk. 22:30. \x*  
\v 3 Niɣ war tessinem ca belli ad neḥkem x lmalakat? Mecḥař ɛad ktar \add i ɣa neḥkem x\add* yinni iǧan n ddunect-a?  
\v 4 Maca mařa din jar awem ict n ddeɛwet x tmesřayin n tudart-a, ma tᵉtteggem inni ɣar iǧa drus n uweqqar waha di tmesmunt ḥima ad ḥekmen?  
\v 5 Qqareɣ awem t ḥima ad tseḍḥam. Ma xenni war dinni ḥed jar awem d amiɣis wenni izemmaren ad iḥkem jar tawmat d umas?  
\v 6 Maca \add řexxu\add*, ijj n tawmat ad icarreɛ ak-d umas u man aya qibač i yinni war yuminen ca.  
\v 7 S uya tḥekkmem x yixef nwem, minzi temcarraɛem jar awem. Mayemmi war tqebbřem ad kenniw ḍeǧen? Mayemmi war tqebbřem ca ad kenniw ɣeccen? \x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt Awřn. 20:22; Mt. 5:39; Rum. 12:17; 1 Ts. 5:15; 1 Bṭ. 3:9. \x*  
\v 8 Maca \add řexxu\add* tᵉtteggem min war iseggden uca tᵉttɣeccam ɛad i aytmatwem.   
\m
\v 9 Ma war tessinem ca belli inni war iseggden war warrten ca Tageldit n AREBBI? War ttraḥem ca di ɣalaṭ! Ayt n farq-ccɣeř, niɣ inni iɛebbden l’aṣnam, niɣ inni itteggen zzina, niɣ inni issexsaran, niɣ zzwameř, \x ◘ \xo 6:9 \xt Gal. 5:19; Afa. 5:5; Asa. 22:15. \x*  
\v 10 niɣ iḍemmaɛen, niɣ iceffaren, niɣ iskarjiyyen, niɣ imceqqafen uřa d ibeɛɛajen war warrten Tageldit n AREBBI.  
\v 11 Tuɣa timesřayin-a řesqent ɣar ca zzaywem, maca aqa kenniw tᵉttwassirdem, aqa tᵉttwaqeddsem, aqa tᵉttwaseggdem s Yisem n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ u s Arruḥ n AREBBI nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt Afa. 2:2; Kul. 3:7; Tit. 3:3; Ɛbr. 10:22. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Arrimet d zzawect n Arruḥ Iqeddsen  
\m
\v 12 Marra timesřayin ḥeǧřent ayi, maca marra war neffɛent. Marra timesřayin ḥeǧřent ayi, maca war d ayi ittḍebbar uřa d ijjen bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 6:12 \xt 1 Kur. 10:23. \x*  
\v 13 Macca i uɛeddis uca aɛeddis i macca, maca AREBBI ad ten ibeṭṭeř s tyuya. Maca arrimet war teǧi i farq-ccɣeř, maca i Siditneɣ, uca Siditneɣ i arrimet.  
\v 14 Maca AREBBI wenni dd-issnekkaren Siditneɣ, ad aneɣ dd-issnekkar s jjehd nnes. \x ◘ \xo 6:14 \xt Rum. 8:11; 2 Kur. 4:14. \x*  
\v 15 Ma war tessinem ca belli arrimat nwem ǧant d iɣezdisen n Lmasiḥ? Ma ad ksiɣ xenni ijj n uɣezdis n Lmasiḥ, maḥend ad t ggeɣ d aɣezdis n ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř? Ɛemmarṣ!  
\v 16 Niɣ war tessinem ca belli wi imunen ak-d temɣart n farq-ccɣeř, aqa-t d ict n arrimet \add akides\add*? Minzi iqqar: ‘Nitni s tnayen ad iřin d ict n arrimet.’ \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt Amz. 2:24; Mt. 19:5, 6; Mk. 10:8; Afa. 5:31 \x*  
\v 17 Maca wenni imunen ak-d Siditneɣ, aqa-t d ijj n arruḥ akides.   
\m
\v 18 Arewřem zi farq-ccɣeř. Kuř ca n ddenb i ittegg bnadem, aqa-t barra i arrimet nnes, maca wenni issefsaden ixef nnes s farq-ccɣeř, aqa netta ixeṭṭa ḍidd i arrimet nnes.  
\v 19 Ma war tessinem ca belli arrimet nwem d zzawect n Arruḥ Iqeddsen wenni daywem iǧan, wenni i ṭṭfem zi AREBBI, u aqa kenniw war teǧim ca i yixef nwem? \x ◘ \xo 6:19 \xt 1 Kur. 3:16; 2 Kur. 6:16; Afa. 2:21; Ɛbr. 3:6; 1 Bṭ. 2:5. \x*  
\v 20 Aqa temmesɣem-dd s ttaman. Semɣarem xenni AREBBI di arrimet nwem u di arruḥ nwem tinni iǧan n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 6:20 \xt 1 Kur. 7:23; Gal. 3:13; Ɛbr. 9:12; 1 Bṭ. 1:18. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 X řemřac  
\m
\v 1 Zi jjihet min d ayi turim, aqa mliḥ i bnadem war ittḥidi ca tamɣart.  
\v 2 Maca zi ssibbet n farq-ccɣeř, kuř aryaz ad yawi tamɣart nnes uca kuř ict n temɣart ad tᵉṭṭef aryaz nnes.  
\v 3 Ejj aryaz ad isscen i temɣart nnes tayri i d as dd-yusin, ammu ɛawed tamɣart i weryaz nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:3 \xt 1 Bṭ. 3:7. \x*  
\v 4 Tamɣart war tᵉttḍebbari ca di arrimet nnes, maca aryaz nnes. Uca ammu ɛawed aryaz war ittḍebbari ca di arrimet nnes, maca tamɣart nnes.  
\v 5 War \add tt\add* qeṭṭɛem ca x wayawya, mɣir mařa tekksem deg wawař ca n umur ḥima ad ceɣřem s uẓummi d tẓaǧit. Awarni man aya munem ɛawed maḥend ad tawyem ariqqi i řemrac, ḥima war kenniw ittjarrib cciṭan zi ssibbet n meẓri n arrimet. \x ◘ \xo 7:5 \xt Yuw. 2:16. \x*  
\v 6 Qqareɣ man aya di ṭṭweɛ n yinni iḍeɛfen, war iǧi s řumur.  
\v 7 Xseɣ ɛad mliḥ mařa marra iwdan ad iřin am necc di tazdugi, maca kuř ijj ɣares tawhibt nnes i d as iwca AREBBI, ijjen ammu, wenneɣni ammu. \x ◘ \xo 7:7 \xt Mt. 19:12; Řex. 26:29; 1 Kur. 12:11. \x*   
\m
\v 8 Maca i yinni war ɣarsen bu temɣart u i tijjař qqareɣ, aqa mliḥ i nitni mařa qqimem am necc.  
\v 9 Maca mařa war zemmaren ad qqimen ṭṭfen di man aya, ejj i-ten ad meřcen, minzi iḥřa ad awyen tamɣart x wecmaḍ n nnecwet. \x ◘ \xo 7:9 \xt 1 Tim. 5:14. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Maca i yinni yiwyen ict n temɣart, umureɣ, war iǧi d necc, maca Sidi inu, belli tamɣart war tbeṭṭi x weryaz. \x ◘ \xo 7:10 \xt Mal. 2:14; Mt. 5:32; 19:9; Mk. 10:11; Lk. 16:18. \x*  
\v 11 Uca mařa tebḍa, ad teqqim břa aryaz, niɣ ad tᵉmmesseṣřeḥ ak-d weryaz nnes, uca aryaz war ittejji tamɣart nnes.   
\m
\v 12 Xenni i inneɣni qqareɣ necc, war iǧi Sidi: Mařa ijj n tawmat ɣares tamɣart war ittimnen, uca nettat teqbeř ad tezdeɣ akides, war tt ineṭṭar ca.  
\v 13 Uca mařa ict n temɣart tenni ɣar iǧa weryaz war yuminen, u netta ixs ad kides izdeɣ, war tsemmeḥ ca nettat deg weryaz nnes.  
\v 14 S minzi aryaz war yuminen ittwaqeddes di temɣart tenni yumnen, uřa d tamɣart war yuminen tᵉttwaqeddes deg weryaz i yumnen, mařa mammec nneɣni ad iřin iḥenjiren nwem d imengas, maca řexxu aqa nitni d imezdagen.   
\m
\v 15 Maca mařa wenni war ittimnen ad iǧef, ejj i-t ad iǧef. Xenni tawmat niɣ tawečmat war ttwaqqnen ca di řḥař nni. Aqa AREBBI iřaɣa aneɣ-dd ɣar řehna.  
\v 16 Minzi manis tessned cem, \add a\add* tamɣart, ad tessnejmed aryaz nnem? Niɣ manis tessned cek, \add a\add* aryaz, ad tessnejmed tamɣart nnec? \x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt 1 Bṭ. 3:1. \x*   
\m
\v 17 Maca kuř ijj am mammec d as iwca SIDI, am mammec i d iřaɣa AREBBI i kuř ijj, ejj i-t ad iddar ammu. Ammu i umureɣ i marra timesmunin.  
\v 18 Mařa ittwařaɣa i weryaz ittwaxetnen \add ɣar umuni ak-d Lmasiḥ\add*, wanita war yarezzu ad dd-idweř ɣar břa axtan nnes, uca mařa ittwařaɣa i ḥed břa axtan, ejj i-t war yarezzu ad t xetnen.  
\v 19 Axtan d walu u břa axtan d walu, maca aḥeṭṭu n tweṣṣa n AREBBI, wah!  
\v 20 Ejj kuř ijjen ad iqqim di třaɣit i zi dd-ittwařaɣa. \x ◘ \xo 7:20 \xt Afa. 4:1; Fil. 1:27; Kul. 1:10; 1 Ts. 2:12. \x*  
\v 21 Mařa tuɣa cek tᵉttwařaɣid-dd d ismeɣ war tessḥissifed ca i man aya, maca mařa tzemmared ad tᵉttwassarḥed, ixḍar xenni s yixef nnec, maḥend ad tsexxared.  
\v 22 Minzi wenni ittwařaɣan di Siditneɣ am tuɣa d ismeɣ, aqa-t d aḥurri n AREBBI, am mammec wenni ittwařaɣan d aḥurri, aqa-t d ismeɣ n Lmasiḥ.  
\v 23 Aqa temmesɣem-dd s ttaman, \add xenni\add* war iɛeddeř ad tiřim ɛad d isemɣan n iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 7:23 \xt 1 Kur. 6:20; Ɛbr. 9:12; 1 Bṭ. 1:18. \x*  
\v 24 \add A\add* aytma, ejj kuř ijjen ad isiɣi ak-d AREBBI deg webrid nni di dd-ittwařaɣa.   
\b  
\m
\v 25 Deg wazzay n tuɛezriya, aqa war ɣari bu řumur n AREBBI, maca ad wceɣ array inu, am wi yiwḍen s arḍa n AREBBI ḥima ad yiři d amtiqqi.  
\v 26 Ittɣiř ayi mliḥ i řeɣben i iǧan di řweqt-a, belli aqa icna i bnadem ad iqqim am iǧa.  
\v 27 Ma třeṣqed di temɣart? War arezzu ca ad \add zzayes\add* tennfekked. Mařa cek war třeṣqed di temɣart? War arezzu x temɣart. \f ◼ \fr 7:27 \ft \+fk Ma cek war třeṣqeḍ di temɣart?\ft  - awař-a ixs ad yini: ‘Ma cek břa tamɣart?’\f*  
\v 28 Maca mařa tiwyed tamɣart, war txeṭṭid. Uca mařa taɛzarect tedweř ɣar weryaz, nettat war txeṭṭi ca. Maca inni \add iqqnen i wayawaya s řemřac\add*, tᵉttraja i-ten řmeḥnet di arrimet, uca xseɣ ad tt xawem kkseɣ.   
\m
\v 29 D man aya i qqareɣ, \add a\add* aytma, aqa řḥař imẓi. S uyenni inni ɣar iǧa temɣart, ejj i-ten ad iřin axmi war ɣarsen teǧi,  
\v 30 inni ittrun axmi war ttrun, inni ifarrḥen axmi war friḥen, inni issaɣen axmi war mellken,  
\v 31 u inni istenfaɛen zi ddunect-a, ittxeṣṣa war ttaggʷijen x ustenfeɛ i dd-ittřiqen, minzi udem n ddunect aya ad iɛdu. \x ◘ \xo 7:31 \xt Ica. 40:6; Yaɛ. 1:10; 4:14; 1 Bṭ. 1:24; 1 Yḥ. 2:17. \x*   
\m
\v 32 S uyenni xseɣ ad tiřim břa amnus, maɣar wenni war ɣares teǧi temɣart, ad ixarreṣ di min iǧan n Sides d mammec ɣa yarḍa Sides. \x ◘ \xo 7:32 \xt 1 Tim. 5:5. \x*  
\v 33 Maca wenni ɣar teǧa temɣart, ad iksi s wemnus i tmesřayin n ddunect-a u mammec ɣa yarḍa tamɣart nnes.   
\m
\v 34 Aqa din ijj n řfarq jar temɣart d teɛzarect. Tenni war ɣar iǧi weryaz ɛemmarṣ, ad txarreṣ di Sides, ḥima ad tiři tqeddes am di arrimet am di arruḥ, maca tenni ɣar teǧa weryaz, ad txarreṣ di tmesřayin n ddunect, i mammec ɣa tarḍa aryaz nnes.  
\v 35 Degga qqareɣ awem-dd i tizi nwem, war iǧi ḥima ad awem ggeɣ řfex, maca \add nniɣ t\add* ḥima ad teqqimen d imtiqqan i Siditwem x ubrid nican, am war tseřhim ak-d ddunect.   
\m
\v 36 Maca mařa ixarreṣ ḥed belli aqa sthezzan zzayes zi ssibbet n yeǧis taɛzarect, tenni x ɛdun wussan n temẓi nnes am war tt issemřec ɛad i weryaz, uca ittɣiř as nican ad tt issemřec, netta war ixeṭṭi ca. Ejj i-tt ad tmeřc.  
\v 37 Maca wi iǧan nican deg wuř nnes, břa ma yuca s uziyyar, uca ɣares ṣṣulṭa x yixef nnes, ikkes deg wuř nnes ad yejj taɛzarect nnes teṣfa, mliḥ i yegga.  
\v 38 S uyenni, wenni issmeřcen yeǧis taɛzarect igga mliḥ, u wenni war issmeǧicen yeǧis taɛzarect, igga mliḥ aṭṭas.   
\m
\v 39 Tamɣart teqqen ɣar weryaz nnes s Ccariɛa min ɣa yekk weryaz nnes iddar, maca mařa aryaz nnes immut, aqa-tt tsarreḥ zzayes, tzemmar ad temřec ak-d wi texs, maca di Siditneɣ waha. \x ◘ \xo 7:39 \xt Rum. 7:2. \x*  
\v 40 Maca necc ɣari, aqa nettat ad tᵉttwabarek ktar mařa teqqim amenni. U aqa Necc ttwařiɣ Arruḥ n AREBBI \add ixeddem\add* ɛawed dayi. \x ◘ \xo 7:40 \xt 1 Ts. 4:8. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 X macca n weysum n tɣarṣin i l’aṣnam  
\m
\v 1 Zi jjihet n tɣarṣin i l’aṣnam, aqa nessen, belli marra ɣarneɣ tussna. Tussna \add maca\add* tᵉttegg tuffet, maca tayri tessyemma.  
\v 2 Mařa din ḥed ittɣiř as belli issen ca, ɛad war issin walu anect mammec ittxeṣṣa ad issen.  
\v 3 Maca mařa ittexs ḥed AREBBI, aqa d wa ittwassen zzayes.   
\m
\v 4 X macca tenni ittwaɣarṣen i l’aṣnam, aqa nessen belli ṣṣanam war iǧi d walu di ddunect, u belli war din iǧi ca AREBBI nneɣni mɣir Ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 8:4 \xt Aɛwd. 4:39; Rum. 14:14; 1 Kur. 10:19; Afa. 4:6. \x*  
\v 5 Xenni, waxxa aqa din inni umi qqaren irebbiten, niɣ deg ujenna niɣ di temmurt - am mammec ǧan din aṭṭas n irebbiten d waṭṭas n isiditen -  
\v 6 i neccin aqa ɣarneɣ ijj n AREBBI, Babatneɣ, maɣar zzayes i dd-usint marra timesřayin u dayes i neǧa, u aqa ɣarneɣ ijj n SIDI, aqa-t d Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, maɣar marra timesřayin ǧant s ufus nnes, uca uřa d neccin aqa s ifassen nnes i neǧa. \x ◘ \xo 8:6 \xt Mal. 2:10; Yḥ. 13:13; 1 Kur. 12:3; Afa. 4:6; Fil. 2:11. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Maca tussna-ya war daysen teǧi marra, minzi din ca n yinni di tnefsect nsen ttᵉtten min ittwaɣarṣen i l’aṣnam, uca \add xenni\add* tᵉttwassexmej \add tnefsect nsen\add* s manayenni, minzi teḍɛef tnefsect nsen. \x ◘ \xo 8:7 \xt 1 Kur. 10:28. \x*  
\v 8 Maca macca war d aneɣ tessiwiḍ ca ɣar AREBBI, minzi mařa necca, aqa war dayneɣ yarenni ca, niɣ mařa war necci, aqa war dayneɣ bu řexṣeṣ. \x ◘ \xo 8:8 \xt Rum. 14:17. \x*  
\v 9 Maca ɣarwem, aqa ttesriḥ nwem war dd-tusi ad tiři d taɛenkrift i yinni iḍeɛfen. \x ◘ \xo 8:9 \xt Gal. 5:13. \x*  
\v 10 S minzi mařa ḥed ittwařa kenniw, inni ɣar teǧa tussna, tᵉttɣimam di zzawect mani ɛebbden l’aṣnam, ma tanefsect nnes, minzi netta iḍɛef, war tᵉttwajbed ca ad tekkar maḥend ad yecc min ɣarṣen i l’aṣnam?  
\v 11 Ammu s tussna nnec ad iweddar wenni iḍeɛfen, wenni i xef immut Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 8:11 \xt Rum. 14:15. \x*  
\v 12 Xmi txeṭṭim ammu x wawmaten nwem uca tessyezzmem tuḍɛeft n tnefsect nsen, aqa txeṭṭim x Lmasiḥ.  
\v 13 S uyenni, mařa macca aqa tarra uma ad innedref, war ttᵉtteɣ aysum ɛemmarṣ, ḥima war ssendrifeɣ ca uma. \x ◘ \xo 8:13 \xt Rum. 14:21; 2 Kur. 11:29. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Ttesriḥ n rrasul  
\m
\v 1 Ma war ǧiɣ d aḥurri? Ma war ǧiɣ d rrasul? Ma war ẓriɣ Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ? Ma war teǧim kenniw d řxedmet inu di Sidi inu? \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt Řex. 9:3, 17; 22:14, 18; 23:11; 1 Kur. 4:15; 15:8; 2 Kur. 12:2. \x*  
\v 2 Mařa war ǧiɣ d rrasul i wenneɣni, i kenniw nican ɛniɣ t, \add wah,\add* kenniw d acemmiɛ n řxedmet inu n rrasul.   
\m
\v 3 Necc arriɣ-dd x yinni xafi iḥekkmen ammu:  
\v 4 Ma war ɣarneɣ bu ttesriḥ ḥima ad necc, ad nsu? \x ◘ \xo 9:4 \xt 1 Kur. 9:14; 1 Ts. 2:6; 2 Ts. 3:9. \x*  
\v 5 Ma war ɣarneɣ bu ttesriḥ ad nawi akidneɣ ict n twečmat d tamɣart am ɛawed rrusul inneɣni d wawmaten n Siditneɣ d Kifa? \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Mt. 8:14. \x*  
\v 6 Niɣ waha Bar-Naba d necc war ɣarneɣ bu ttesriḥ ḥima war nxeddem?  
\v 7 Man wen i ɣa ixeddmen di řɛeskar ad ixeǧeṣ řmunet i yixef nnes? Man wen i ɣa iẓẓun ict n tzayart deg ijj n umarjeɛ n uḍiř, war ittett ca zi řɣiǧet nnes? Niɣ man wen i ɣa yarekkwesen ict n tḥimart, war isess ca aɣi n tḥimart? \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Yḥ. 21:15; 1 Kur. 3:6, 7, 8; 2 Kur. 10:4; 1 Bṭ. 5:2. \x*  
\v 8 Ma qqareɣ man aya am bnadem \add waha\add*? Xzar, uřa d Ccariɛa teqqar aya!  
\v 9 Minzi tura di Ccariɛa n Musa: “War ttegg tacmant i uyenduz issarwaten.” Ma AREBBI iḥeṭṭa x iyenduzen s tidett? \x ◘ \xo 9:9 \xt Aɛwd. 25:4; 1 Tim. 5:18. \x*  
\v 10 Nessen aqa inna i-t di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ u man aya tura di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ, minzi wenni icarrzen, ad icarz s usitem u wenni issarwaten, ad issarwat s usitem ad ɣares yiři ṣṣabet.   
\m
\v 11 Mařa neccin aqa nzarreɛ daywem min iǧan n Arruḥ, xenni ma d aṭṭas mařa nemjar zzaywem \add ca\add* zi min iǧan n temmurt? \x ◘ \xo 9:11 \xt Rum. 15:27; Gal. 6:6. \x*  
\v 12 Mařa inneɣni ɣarsen ttesriḥ-a xawem, \add maḥend ad carcen di min iǧan nwem\add*, mayemmi neccin ktar lla? Maca neccin war nesstenfiɛ zi ttesriḥ-a, maca neksi marra, ḥima war nᵉttegg uřa d ict n tɛenkrift i Řexbar Aṣebḥan n Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 9:12 \xt Řex. 20:33; 2 Kur. 11:9; 12:13. \x*  
\v 13 Ma war tessinem ca belli inni ittsexxaren deg Uqeddas ad ttwarezqen zi \add min iǧan deg\add* Uqeddas? Uca inni ittsexxaren ɣar uɛalṭar ad ṭṭfen tasɣart nsen zeg uɛalṭar? \x ◘ \xo 9:13 \xt Aɛwd. 18:1. \x*  
\v 14 Ammu ɛawed yumur Siditneɣ i yinni ittbarrḥen Řexbar nnes Aṣebḥan, aqa ad ddaren zi Řexbar Aṣebḥan. \x ◘ \xo 9:14 \xt Lawi 19:13; Aɛwd. 24:14; 25:4; Mt. 10:10; Lk. 10:7; 1 Tim. 5:18. \x*   
\m
\v 15 Maca necc war sstenfiɛeɣ zeg uřa d ict zi tmesřayin-a. U necc war t uriɣ ca, ḥima ad ittwagg man aya i necc, meɛlik ufiɣ ad mmteɣ x usebḍeř n usemɣar inu s ca n yijjen.  
\v 16 Xenni mařa necc ttbarrḥeɣ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan, necc war ɣari ca min di ɣa ssemɣareɣ, minzi ittxeṣṣa ayi man aya. Ayeḥḥat xafi, mařa war ttbarrḥeɣ ca s Řexbar Aṣebḥan!  
\v 17 S uyenni, mařa ggiɣ tt s řxaḍar inu, ad ɣari tiři řmunet, maca mařa war tt tteggiɣ s řxaḍar, aqa ad iqqim uwekkeř deg ufus inu.  
\v 18 Man ten qaɛ iǧan d řmunet inu? Aqa-tt d ta: am ttbarrḥeɣ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan ad sseḥḍareɣ Řexbar Aṣebḥan n Lmasiḥ baṭeř, war kessiɣ ca ttesriḥ inu i dayi iwca \add Arebbi\add* di L’Injil.   
\m
\v 19 Necc, umi qqimeɣ ttwaḥarreɣ zi marra, aqa arreɣ ixef inu d amsexxar n marra, ḥima ad arebḥeɣ aṭṭas \add n iwdan\add*.  
\v 20 I Wudayen dewřeɣ am Wuday ḥima ad arebḥeɣ Udayen, i yinni iǧan sadu Ccariɛa dewřeɣ am yinni sadu Ccariɛa, ḥima ad arebḥeɣ inni iǧan sadu Ccariɛa. \x ◘ \xo 9:20 \xt Řex. 16:3; 18:18; 21:23. \x*  
\v 21 I yinni iǧan břa Ccariɛa dewřeɣ am wenni břa Ccariɛa - war ǧiɣ břa Ccariɛa qibač i AREBBI, maca aqa-yi ddareɣ di Ccariɛa n Lmasiḥ - ḥima ad arebḥeɣ inni iǧan břa Ccariɛa. \x ◘ \xo 9:21 \xt Gal. 2:3. \x*  
\v 22 Tuɣa ayi ḍeɛfeɣ ɣar yinni iḍeɛfen, ḥima ad arebḥeɣ inni iḍeɛfen. Aqa dewřeɣ d marra i marra, ḥima beɛda ad wceɣ Tudart i marra. \x ◘ \xo 9:22 \xt Rum. 15:1; 1 Kur. 10:33; Gal. 6:1. \x*  
\v 23 Man aya tteggeɣ, ḥima ad ṭṭfeɣ tasɣart di Řexbar Aṣebḥan.   
\m
\v 24 Ma war tessinem ca belli inni itteggen tḥamat n tazřa di řmeřɛeb, marra nican aqa ttazzřen, maca ijjen zzaysen i ɣa yarebḥen waha? Xenni azzřem kenniw ammu ař d ɣa tarebḥem. \x ◘ \xo 9:24 \xt Gal. 2:2; 5:7; Fil. 2:16; 2 Tim. 4:7; Ɛbr. 6:18. \x*  
\v 25 Maca kuř aryaz i itteggen ict n tḥamet, iḥekkem x yixef nnes di marra. Nitni uzzřen ḥima ad arebḥen ijj n ttaj ifenna, maca neccin ḥima ad narbeḥ ijj n ttaj war ifenni. \x ◘ \xo 9:25 \xt 2 Tim. 2:4; 4:8; 1 Bṭ. 1:4; 5:4. \x*  
\v 26 S uyenni necc war ttizzřeɣ ca amenni waha, war ttmenɣiɣ am wenni iccaten di řeɛwin,  
\v 27 maca ttmarrateɣ arrimet inu, ad as qetmareɣ, ḥima necc war ttwassuffuɣeɣ ca barra awarni řami barrḥeɣ inneɣni.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\s1 Ijj n weɛřem zeg umezruy n řgens n Israil  
\m
\v 1 \add A\add* aytma, xseɣ ad tessnem, belli řejdud nneɣ tuɣa aten marra sadu useynu uca marra cuqen di řebḥar, \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt Uf. 13:21; 14:22; Řxř. 9:18; Aɛwd. 1:33; Yac. 4:23; Naḥ. 9:12, 19; Izhd. 78:13, 14; 105:39. \x*  
\v 2 uca marra ttwassɣeḍṣen di Musa deg useynu u di řebḥar, \x ◘ \xo 10:2 \xt Uf. 13:20-22, 14:19, 20. \x*  
\v 3 uca marra ccin macca taruḥect d ict, \x ◘ \xo 10:3 \xt Uf. 16:15. \x*  
\v 4 uca marra swin tisessit taruhect d ict, minzi nitni swin zeg weẓru n Arruḥ wenni tuɣa akidsen, u aẓru nni tuɣa-t d Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 10:4 \xt Uf. 17:6; Řxř. 20:11; Izhd. 78:15; Yḥ. 7:37-39.\x*  
\v 5 Maca AREBBI tuɣa war yarḍi x wezyen ameqqran zzaysen, minzi aqa aten wḍan di řexřa. \x ◘ \xo 10:5 \xt Řxř. 26:65. \x*   
\m
\v 6 Man aya imsar d lmital i neccin, ḥima war dayneɣ ittiři mmeẓri di min iɛeffnen, am mammec tuɣa nitni daysen meẓri. \x ◘ \xo 10:6 \xt Řxř. 11:4,33; Izhd. 106:14. \x*  
\v 7 Ejj aneɣ war ndikkwiř ca ad neɛbed l’aṣnam, am \add ca\add* zzaysen, am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Řgens iqqim ḥima ad icc ad issu\qt*  
\m \qt uca kkaren ḥima ad iraren.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:7 \xt Uf. 32:6. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 War iɛeddeř ad nessefsad ixef nneɣ, am \add ca\add* zzaysen. Aqa mmuten din třata u-ɛicrin-ařef deg ijj n wass. \x ◘ \xo 10:8 \xt Řxř. 25:1, 9; Izhd. 106:29. \x*  
\v 9 War iɛeddeř ad njarreb Lmasiḥ, am mammec jarrben \add t\add* \add ca\add* zzaysen uca ttwahelken s ifiɣran. \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt Řxř. 21:5; Izhd. 106:14. \x*  
\v 10 War iɛeddeř ɛawed ad nessfixex am mammec \add ca\add* zzaysen ssfixixen, uca \add xenni\add* ttwahellken s ufus n umhellek. \x ◘ \xo 10:10 \xt Uf. 16:2; 17:2; Řxř. 14:36; Izhd. 106:25. \x*  
\v 11 Marra min d asen imsaren, aqa t d lmital i neccin, uca tura d aɛřam i neccin mixef dd-yusa uneggar n zzmanat. \x ◘ \xo 10:11 \xt Rum. 15:4; 1 Kur. 9:10; Fil. 4:5; Ɛbr. 10:25. \x*   
\m
\v 12 S uyenni wenni umi ittɣiř aqa ibedd, ejj i-t ad iḥḍa war iweṭṭi.  
\v 13 War xawem ittekk ujarreb mɣir wenni i ɣa yawḍen ɣar iwdan. \add Maca\add* AREBBI dayes řaman. Netta war kenniw ittejji ad tᵉttwajarrbem sennej i min tzemmarem, maca Netta ittic uffuɣ ak-d ujarreb nwem, ḥima ad tzemmarem ad tarbum \add aɣekkwi\add*. \x ◘ \xo 10:13 \xt 1 Kur. 1:8; 1 Ts. 5:24; 2 Bṭ. 2:9. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tazewḍa n Siditneɣ  
\m
\v 14 S uya, imɛizzen inu, arewřem zeg uɛbad i l’aṣnam.  
\v 15 Ssawařeɣ \add akidwem\add* axmi ssawařeɣ ak-d imiɣisen. Ḥekmem kenniw \add xenni\add* x min d awem qqareɣ.  
\v 16 Řkas n uqadi nni nettbarak, ma war iǧi d tamunt ak-d Idammen n Lmasiḥ? Aɣrum nni ntareẓẓa, ma war iǧi d tamunt ak-d Arrimet n Lmasiḥ?  
\v 17 Am mammec iǧa aɣrum d ijjen, ammu marra neccin d ict n Arrimet, minzi marra neccin neṭṭef zeg ijj n weɣrum. \x ◘ \xo 10:17 \xt Rum. 12:5; 1 Kur. 12:27. \x*   
\m
\v 18 Xzarem ɣar Israil ɛlaḥsab arrimet! Ma inni ittetten zi tɣarṣa war ɣarsen acrac ak-d uɛalṭar? \f ◼ \fr 10:18 \ft \+fk aɛalṭar\ft  - niɣ: ‘řmedbeḥ’.\f*  
\v 19 Min ɣa iniɣ di man aya? Ma belli min immewcen d taɣarṣt i l’aṣnam d ca, niɣ belli l’aṣnam d ca? Lla. \x ◘ \xo 10:19 \xt 1 Kur. 8:4. \x*  
\v 20 Min wcin lkuffar d taɣarṣt, wehhben tt i ccwaṭen, war iǧi i AREBBI. Uca necc war xseɣ ad tcarcem ak-d ccwaṭen. \f ◼ \fr 10:20 \ft \+fk ccwaṭen\ft  - niɣ: ‘ccayaṭin’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:20 \xt Lawi 17:7; Aɛwd. 32:17. \x*  
\v 21 War tzemmarem ad teswem řkas n Siditneɣ uřa d řkas n ccwaṭen, uca war tzemmarem ad tcarcem tazewḍa n Siditneɣ uřa d tazewḍa n ccwaṭen. \f ◼ \fr 10:21 \ft \+fk taẓewḍa\ft  - niɣ: ‘missa’.\f*  
\v 22 Niɣ ad nessekkar tusmi n Siditneɣ? Ma nejhed xas neccin?   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tiřelli n řmumen  
\m
\v 23 Marra ittḥeǧeř ayi, maca marra war ineffeɛ. Marra ittheǧeř, maca marra war ibenni. \x ◘ \xo 10:23 \xt 1 Kur. 6:12. \x*  
\v 24 Uřa d ijj war yarezzu ca tizi nnes \add waha\add*, maca \add ejj\add* kuř ijj \add ad yarzu\add* ɛawed tenni n wenni d as yudsen. \x ◘ \xo 10:24 \xt 1 Kur. 13:5; Fil. 2:4. \x*   
\m
\v 25 Marra min ittmenzan di ssuq n igezzaren, tzemmarem ad t teccem břa aseqsi di ṭṭweɛ n tnefsect,  
\v 26 minzi i SIDI umi ɣar teǧa temmurt d uɛemmar nnes. \x ◘ \xo 10:26 \xt Uf. 19:5; Izhd. 24:1; 50:12, 89:12. \x*  
\v 27 Mařa ca n yijjen zeg lkuffar, iɛarḍ i kenniw u texsem ad traḥem, ccem zi marra min d awem i d ɣa issars, war tesseqsim ca x ssibbet n tnefsect. \f ◼ \fr 10:27 \ft \+fk tanefsect\ft  - niɣ: ‘ḍḍamir’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:27 \xt Lk. 10:7; 1 Kur. 8:7. \x*  
\v 28 Maca mařa ḥed inna awem: “Degga ittwaɣarṣ i l’aṣnam!”, war zzayes tᵉttettem di ṭṭweɛ n wenni d awem iɛeřmen uřa di ṭṭweɛ n tnefsect.  
\v 29 Mařa necc nniɣ \add di ṭṭweɛ n\add* ‘tnefsect’, war ɛniɣ tanefsect nwem, maca tenni n wenneɣni. Minzi mayemmi ɣa tᵉttwaḥakem třelli inu s tnefsect n wenneɣni?  
\v 30 Mařa necc carceɣ s uweqqar \add ɣar umensi\add*, mayemmi ɣa ttwaceqqfeɣ di ssibbet mixef ttqadiɣ? \x ◘ \xo 10:30 \xt Rum. 14:6; 1 Tim. 4:3. \x*   
\m
\v 31 Xenni mařa tᵉttettem niɣ tsessem niɣ tᵉtteggem ca n řḥajjet nneɣni, ggem tt marra i uɛuǧi n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 10:31 \xt Kul. 3:17. \x*  
\v 32 War ttiřim d taɛenkrift i Wudayen niɣ i Iramiyyen uřa i tmesmunt n AREBBI, \x ◘ \xo 10:32 \xt Rum. 14:13. \x*  
\v 33 am mammec uřa d necc arezzuɣ ad dd-aseɣ ak-d marra di kuřci, war arezzuɣ min iǧan i tizi inu, maca min iǧan i tizi n waṭṭas, ḥima ad ɣarsen tiři Tudart. \x ◘ \xo 10:33 \xt 1 Kur. 9:22. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Aryaz d temɣart di Tmesmunt n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ  
\m
\v 1 Ḍfarem ayi-dd am mammec ḍfareɣ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt 1 Kur. 4:16; Fil. 3:17; 1 Ts. 1:6; 2 Ts. 3:9. \x*  
\v 2 Ssemɣareɣ kenniw, \add a\add* aytma inu, minzi tᵉttfekkarem dayi di marra uca tᵉtteṭṭfem di tewṣeyyat, am mammec d awem tent wciɣ.   
\m
\v 3 Maca xseɣ ad tessnem belli Lmasiḥ d Azeǧif n kuř aryaz uca aryaz d azeǧif n temɣart, uca AREBBI d Azeǧif n Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 11:3 \xt Yḥ. 14:28; 1 Kur. 3:23; 15:27; Afa. 5:23. \x*  
\v 4 Kuř aryaz wenni ittẓaǧan niɣ ittnabben am iřeḥḥef x uzeǧif nnes, ifeṭṭeḥ azeǧif nnes.  
\v 5 Maca kuř tamɣart tenni ittẓaǧan niɣ ittnabben am tessɛarra uzeǧif nnes, tfeṭṭeḥ azeǧif nnes, minzi nettat am tenni iḥeffen azeǧif nnes.  
\v 6 Minzi mařa tamɣart war třeḥḥif, ejj i-tt ad tḥeff ɛawed. Maca mařa d řefḍiḥet i temɣart mařa tqess \add acuwwaf\add* niɣ tḥeff, ḥsen mařa třeḥḥef. \x ◘ \xo 11:6 \xt Řxř. 5:18; Aɛwd. 22:5. \x*  
\v 7 Minzi aryaz war itteḥwiji ca ad iřeḥḥef azeǧif nnes, minzi netta d ṣṣifet d aɛuǧi n AREBBI, maca tamɣart teǧa d aɛuǧi n weryaz. \x ◘ \xo 11:7 \xt Amz. 1:26, 27; 5:1; 9:6; Kul. 3:10. \x*  
\v 8 Minzi aryaz war iǧi ca zi temɣart, maca tamɣart zeg weryaz. \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Amz. 2:18, 21. \x*  
\v 9 Aryaz ɛawed war dd-ixřiq ca i temɣart, maca tamɣart i weryaz.  
\v 10 S uyenni ittxeṣṣa as i temɣart ad ɣares tiři ṣṣulṭa x uzeǧif nnes x ssibbet n lmalakat.  
\v 11 Maca di Siditneɣ aryaz war \add iǧi\add* břa tamɣart, uřa d tamɣart war \add teǧi\add* břa aryaz.  
\v 12 Minzi am mammec tamɣart tusa-dd zeg weryaz, amenni ɛawed iǧa weryaz s temɣart, maca marra min iǧan aqa-t zi AREBBI.  
\v 13 Ḥekmem kenniw simant nwem: Ma tusa-dd x temɣart ad teẓẓaǧ i AREBBI am tessɛarra i uzeǧif nnes?  
\v 14 Ma tubbart simant nnes war d awem tesscan belli acuwwaf d azirar d řefḍiḥet i weryaz?  
\v 15 Maca i temɣart d aɛuǧi mařa ɣares yiři ucuwwaf d azirar, minzi immewc as ucuwwaf am uřeḥḥaf.  
\v 16 Maca mařa ixs ḥed ad ixarweḍ man aya, neccin war ɣarneɣ bu tnamit nni uřa d timesmunin n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 11:16 \xt 1 Tim. 6:4. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Amensi Iqeddsen  
\m
\v 17 Weṣṣiɣ kenniw x tmesřayin-a \add řexxu\add*, aqa war d awem tteggeɣ ccan, minzi war tuyurem ɣar zzat, maca tuyurem ɣar ḍeffar.  
\v 18 \add Ɣar umezwar\add*, mařa tmunem am tmesmunt, sřiɣ aqa din jar awem amsebḍi, u man aya zemmareɣ ad t amneɣ i ijj n wezyen,  
\v 19 s minzi ittxeṣṣa ad din iřin jar awem imcubbcen, ḥima ad iban man wen zzaywem i iǧan d amqeǧeb. \x ◘ \xo 11:19 \xt Mt. 18:7; Lk. 17:1; Řex. 20:30; 1 Yḥ. 2:19. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Xmi ttmunam, war tᵉttettem d tsessem am mammec icuwwar deg wass n Siditneɣ, \f ◼ \fr 11:20 \ft \+fk ass n Siditneɣ\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini ass n umensi n SIDI.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:20 \xt Lk. 22:14-20. \x*  
\v 21 maca kuř ijjen ittett amensi nnes i yixef nnes, \add uca xenni\add* ijjen nneɣni dayes řaẓ uca nneɣni iscara.  
\v 22 Ma war ɣarwem tudrin mani ɣa teccem u mani ɣa teswem? Niɣ tesseḥqaram tamesmunt n AREBBI uca tessḥeccamem inni war ɣar iǧi ca? Min d awem i ɣa iniɣ? Ma ad awem ggeɣ ccan? \add Lla,\add* war d awem tteggeɣ ccan!   
\m
\v 23 Minzi min ṭṭfeɣ zi Siditneɣ, ssiwḍeɣ awem t-i-dd, aqa Siditneɣ Yasuɛ di ǧiřet i di ittwaɣdar, iksi aɣrum, \x ◘ \xo 11:23 \xt Mt. 26:26; Mk. 14:22; Lk. 22:19. \x*  
\v 24 ibarek, yarẓa i-t, inna: “Ksim, ta d Arrimet inu i xawem ittwarẓen, ggem aya ammu i řidaret xafi!” \x ◘ \xo 11:24 \xt Lk. 22:19\x*  
\v 25 Uca ammu awarni amensi iwca řkas, inna:  
\b  
\m \qt “Řkas-a d Řɛahd n Jdid\qt*  
\m \qt deg Idammen inu.\qt*  
\m \qt Ggem aya,\qt*  
\m \qt mecḥař ma zzayes teswim,\qt*  
\m \qt i řiḍaret xafi.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:25 \xt Irm. 31:31; Mt. 26:28, Mk. 14:24, Lk. 22:20, 1 Kur. 11:25, 2 Kur. 3:6, Ɛbr. 8:6, 8, 13; 9:15; 12:24\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 26 S minzi mecḥař ma i ɣa teccem aɣrum-a u ad teswem zi řkas-a, aqa tᵉttidarem řmewt n Siditneɣ ař dd ɣa yas. \x ◘ \xo 11:26 \xt Yḥ. 14:3; Řex. 1:11. \x*   
\m
\v 27 S uyenni man wen i ɣa iccen aɣrum n SIDI uca ad isu zi řkas nnes, \add am\add* war ittiři s usdaheǧi i man aya, ad yiři s umarwas i Idammen n SIDI u i Arrimet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 11:27 \xt Řxř. 9:10, 13; Yḥ. 6:51, 63, 64; 13:27; 1 Kur. 10:21. \x*  
\v 28 S uyenni ejj kuř ijj ad iqeǧeb ixef nnes, uca ejj i-t ad icc xenni zeg weɣrum u ad isu zi řkas. \x ◘ \xo 11:28 \xt 2 Kur. 13:5. \x*  
\v 29 Minzi wi ɣa iccen d wi ɣa iswen am war isdiheǧ, aqa netta ad issiweḍ řḥukm ɣar ixef nnes am ittett u am isess, minzi netta war ifarrez ca Arrimet n SIDI.  
\v 30 S uyenni aqa din aṭṭas n yinni iḍeɛfen d yinni iheřcen jar awem uca aṭṭas dewřen ttᵉṭṭṣen \add iḍeṣ n řmewt\add*.   
\m
\v 31 Maca mařa neḥkem x ixef nneɣ, xenni war nettwaḥakem. \x ◘ \xo 11:31 \xt Izhd. 32:5; Awřn. 18:17. \x*  
\v 32 Maca mařa nettwaḥkem zi Siditneɣ, aqa nettwarebba, ḥima war nettwaḥakem ca ak-d ddunect.  
\v 33 Zi řexxu, \add a\add* aytma, xmi ɣa tmunem ḥima ad teccem, rajam ijjen wenneɣni.  
\v 34 Mařa ḥed dayes řaẓ, ejj i-t ad icc di taddart nnes, ḥima war tᵉttmunem i ccreɛ. Min iqqimen, ad t ɛedřeɣ xmi dd ɣa yaseɣ.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Timewca n Arruḥ  
\m
\v 1 X tmesřayin n arruḥ, \add a\add* aytma, xseɣ ad tessnem,  
\v 2 tuɣa kenniw d lkuffar u tᵉttwanedhem ɣar l’aṣnam ignawen břa ma tucim.  
\v 3 S uyenni ssaregbeɣ kenniw, aqa war din uřa d ijjen wenni i ɣa issiwřen s Arruḥ n AREBBI, ad yini: ‘Aqa ittwanɛeř Yasuɛ!’, u war din uřa d ijjen wenni i ɣa yinin: ‘Yasuɛ d SIDI!’, mɣir s Arruḥ Iqeddsen waha. \x ◘ \xo 12:3 \xt Mk. 9:39; Yḥ. 13:13; 1 Kur. 8:6. \x*   
\m
\v 4 Aqa din tiwhibin ifarzen, maca Arruḥ aqa-t d Ijj. \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt Rum. 12:6; 1 Bṭ. 4:10. \x*  
\v 5 U aqa din řexdayem n tsexxart ifarzen, maca SIDI aqa-t d Ijj.  
\v 6 Uca aqa din řeɛjayeb ifarzen, maca AREBBI aqa-t d Ijj, d Wenni itteggen marra di marra bnadem.  
\v 7 Maca asargeb n Arruḥ ad immewc i kuř ijj ḥima ad t iɛawen.   
\m
\v 8 Aqa s Arruḥ immewc i yijjen awař n tiɣit, i wenneɣni awař n tussna s Arruḥ \add d ijjen\add*, \x ◘ \xo 12:8 \xt Uf. 31:3; 35;13; Ica. 11:2; Kul. 1:9\x*  
\v 9 i wenneɣni l’iman s Arruḥ, i wenneɣni tawhibt i usgenfi s Arruḥ \add d ijjen\add*,  
\v 10 i wenneɣni maḥend ad igg řeɛjayeb, i wenneɣni mahend ad inebb, i wenneɣni řfarz n arruḥat, i wenneɣni \bd ɛřam kuř iřsawen\bd* uca i wenneɣni afessar n iřsawen.  
\v 11 Maca man aya marra ittegg i-t Arruḥ d Ijjen, wenni ibeṭṭan i kuř ijj anect mammec ixs Netta. \x ◘ \xo 12:11 \xt Rum. 12:3, 6; 1 Kur. 7:7; 2 Kur. 10:13; Afa. 4:7. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Arrimet n Lmasiḥ d icten  
\m
\v 12 Minzi am arrimet aqa-tt d ict u ɣares aṭṭas n iɣezdisen, ɛad aqa aten marra d iɣezdisen n ict n arrimet. Waxxa nitni deg waṭṭas, aqa tteggen ict n arrimet waha, \add uca\add* ammu \add i teǧa tmesřact\add* uřa ak-d Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 12:12 \xt Rum. 12:4, 5; Afa. 4:16. \x*  
\v 13 Minzi nettwasseɣḍeṣ marra s yijj n Arruḥ deg ict n Arrimet, niɣ Udayen niɣ Iramiyyen niɣ isemɣan niɣ iḥurriyyen, uca marra neccin nsu zeg ijj n Arruḥ. \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt Yḥ. 7:37-39; Gal. 3:28. \x*  
\v 14 Uřa d arrimet war teǧi ca s ijj n uɣezdis \add waha\add*, maca s waṭṭas n iɣezdisen.  
\v 15 Mařa aḍar ad ini: “Minzi war ǧiɣ d afus, war ǧiɣ zi arrimet!”, ma xenni war ittiři zi arrimet?”  
\v 16 Uca mařa amezzuɣ inna: “Minzi war ǧiɣ d tiṭṭ, war ǧiɣ zi arrimet!”, ma xenni war ittiři zi arrimet?  
\v 17 Mařa marra arrimet tuɣa-tt d tiṭṭ, manis d ikka useǧi? Mařa marra \add arrimet\add* tuɣa-tt d aseǧi, manis d ikka ucemmi?   
\m
\v 18 Maca řexxu AREBBI igga iɣezdisen di arrimet, kuř ijj zzaysen am mammec ixs Netta.  
\v 19 Minzi mařa marra tuɣa d ijj n uɣezdis, mani teǧa arrimet xenni?  
\v 20 Maca řexxu aqa din aṭṭas n iɣezdisen, maca d ict n arrimet waha.  
\v 21 Tiṭṭ war tzemmar ad tini i ufus: “War cek ḥwijeɣ ca!”, niɣ ɛawed azeǧif i iḍaren: “War kenniw ḥwijeɣ ca!”  
\v 22 Maca s řɛeks iɣezdisen n arrimet inni nḥesseb ḍeɛfen, aqa nitni ttwaḥdajen aṭṭas.  
\v 23 \add Iɣezdisen\add* nni n arrimet i d aneɣ ittɣiřen d imuqřiřen, nᵉttegg asen ccan ktar, uca iɣezdisen inni ittawyen aseḍḥi, ad asen nessḥinneb s waṭṭas n řehzuṭ.  
\v 24 Minzi iɣezdisen nneɣ nni ɣar iǧa řehzuṭ, war ḥdajen man aya, maɣar AREBBI igga arrimet, uca i iɣezdisen i iǧan d qell, iwca asen ccan ktar,  
\v 25 ḥima war ittiři ubeṭṭu di arrimet, maca iɣezdisen ad wcen taynit ijjen i wenneɣni deg uqaren d ijjen.  
\v 26 Mařa ijj n uɣezdis tᵉttekk xas tamara, marra \add iɣezdisen\add* ad ksin tamara akides, u mařa ijj n uɣezdis ifarḥ, ad farḥen marra \add iɣezdisen\add* akides.  
\v 27 Kenniw d Arrimet n Lmasiḥ d iɣezdisen deg wemcan i d awem \add ittwaggen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 12:27 \xt Rum. 12:5; Afa. 1:23; 4:12; 5:23; Kul. 1:24. \x*   
\m
\v 28 Zeɛma AREBBI aqa igga di tmesmunt d amezwaru rrusul, awarni asen inabiyyen, awarni asen imesɣaren, awarni asen inni itteggen řeɛjayeb, awarni asen tiwhibin n usgenfi, inni itticen afus, inni iḍebbaren uca uřa d ɛřam kuř iřsawen. \x ◘ \xo 12:28 \xt Afa. 4:11; 2:20. \x*  
\v 29 Ma zeɛma marra nitni d rrusul? Ma marra d inabiyyen? Ma marra d imesɣaren? Ma marra nitni tteggen řeɛjayeb?  
\v 30 Ma marra ɣarsen tiwhibin n usgenfi? Ma ssawařen marra s iřsawen? Ma ttfessaren marra \add iřsawen\add*?  
\v 31 Maca mařa tarzum xenni di tewhibin timeqqranin \add qaɛ\add*, aqa necc ad awem ssecneɣ ijj n webrid yuɛřan.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Tayri  
\m
\v 1 \qt “Maɛlik necc ssawařeɣ\qt*  
\m \qt s iřsawen n iwdan d lmalakat,\qt*  
\m \qt maca war ɣari bu tayri,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa dewřeɣ d nnḥas ittentunen,\qt*  
\m \qt niɣ d aǧun iddendunen.\qt*   
\m
\v 2 \qt Maɛlik ɣari tawhibt maḥend ad nebbeɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt fehhmeɣ marra řesrar\qt*  
\m \qt u ɣari marra tussna d marra l’iman\qt*  
\m \qt ař d ssmuṭṭiyeɣ idurar,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maca\+tl* war d ayi teǧi tayri,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl xenni\+tl* necc d walu i ǧiɣ.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 13:2 \xt Mt. 7:22; 17:20; 21:21; Mk. 11:23; Lk. 17:6; Rum. 12:7. \x*   
\m
\v 3 \qt Meɛlik bḍiɣ marra agřa inu\qt*  
\m \qt d macca x imezřaḍ,\qt*  
\m \qt maɛlik wciɣ arrimet inu\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad tt sscemḍen,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maca\+tl* war dayi teǧi tayri,\qt*  
\m \qt war d ayi tneffeɛ di walu.\qt*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Tayri teǧa ɣares ttasiɛ n řxaḍar d řeḍrafet,\qt*  
\m \qt tayri war dayes bu tusmi,\qt*  
\m \qt tayri war tᵉttfeyyec s yixef nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt war dayes bu nnfaxet,\qt* \f ◼ \fr 13:4 \ft \+fk nnfaxet\ft  -niɣ: ‘ttakebbur’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 13:4 \xt Awřn. 10:12; 1 Bṭ. 4:8. \x*   
\m
\v 5 \qt Tayri war tᵉttegg bu řefḍiḥet,\qt*  
\m \qt war tarezzu tizi nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt war tᵉttwassarzag,\qt*  
\m \qt uca war tᵉttxemmam di min iǧan d aɛeffan.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 13:5 \xt 1 Kur. 10:24; Fil. 2:4. \x*   
\m
\v 6 \qt aqa war tfarreḥ ca zi řɣecc,\qt*  
\m \qt maca tfarreḥ zi tidett.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt 2 Yḥ. 4. \x*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Aqa tṣebber di marra,\qt*  
\m \qt tᵉttamen di marra,\qt*  
\m \qt tessatem marra,\qt*  
\m \qt uca tarebbu marra.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Tayri war tfenni ɛemmarṣ,\qt*  
\m \qt maca awařen n nnubuwat\qt*  
\m \qt ad ɣarsen yiři uneggar,\qt*  
\m \qt iřsawen ad gnun,\qt*  
\m \qt u tussna ad tebḍeř.\qt*   
\m
\v 9 \qt Minzi aqa nessen ɣar ijj n uɣezdis \+tl waha\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt uca nettnabb mɣir ijj n wezyen,\qt*   
\m
\v 10 \qt maca xmi dd ɣa tas řekmaret\qt*  
\m \qt řexdenni min iǧan ɣar ijj n wezyen ad ibḍeř.\qt*   
\m
\v 11 \qt Řami tuɣa ayi d aḥenjir,\qt*  
\m \qt ssiwřeɣ am uḥenjir,\qt*  
\m \qt fekkareɣ am uḥenjir,\qt*  
\m \qt xarṣeɣ am uḥenjir,\qt*  
\m \qt maca řami dewřeɣ d aryaz,\qt*  
\m \qt jjiɣ \+tl awarni ayi\+tl* min iǧan n uḥenjir.\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt Řexxu nettwařa s ict n tisit \+tl ibarcnen\+tl* \qt*  
\m \qt ɣar ijj n warwas,\qt*  
\m \qt maca xenni ad nẓar tifras ɣar tifras.\qt*  
\m \qt Řexxu ssneɣ ɣar ijj n wezyen \+tl waha\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt maca xenni ad ssneɣ\qt*  
\m \qt mammec tuɣa ttwassneɣ necc.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 13:12 \xt 2 Kur. 3:18. \x*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Maɣar třata-ya ad qqimen:\qt*  
\m \qt l’iman, asitem d tayri,\qt*  
\m \qt maca ameqqran nsen aqa-tt d tayri.”\qt*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Nnubuwa d řhard s iřsawen  
\m
\v 1 Ḍfarem tayri u njebdem ɣar tewhibin n Arruḥ, d amezwaru ḥima ad tnebbam. \f ◼ \fr 14:1 \ft \+fk tayri\ft  - niɣ: ‘řemḥibbet’.\f*  
\v 2 Minzi wenni issawařen s iřsawen \add nneɣni\add*, war issiwiř ca i iwdan, maca i AREBBI, minzi uřa d ijj war d as ifehhem, maca issawař řesrar s Arruḥ.  
\v 3 Maca wenni ittnabben, issawař ɣar yewdan, ḥima ad ten ibna, ad ten isejjeɛ, ad ten issfewwej.  
\v 4 Wenni issawařen s yijj n iřes \add nneɣni\add*, ibenna ixef nnes, maca wenni ittnabben ibenna tamesmunt.  
\v 5 Iwa xseɣ marra kenniw ad tessiwřem s iřsawen \add nneɣni\add*, maca mliḥ ɛad ad tnebbam, minzi amenzu wi ittnebban x wi issiwřen s iřsawen \add nneɣni\add*, mɣir mařa wanita ad \add t\add* ifessar, minzi mařa ifessar ad tᵉttwabna tmesmunt.   
\m
\v 6 Xenni řexxu, \add a\add* aytma, mařa usiɣ-dd ɣarwem uca ad kiwem ssiwřeɣ s iřsawen \add nneɣni\add*, man nnfeɛ i ɣarwem i ɣa yawyeɣ mařa war d awem ssiwřeɣ ca s usargeb niɣ s tussna niɣ s ijj n wawař i ɣa nebbeɣ niɣ s useřmed?  
\v 7 Maɣar uřa d řeḥwayec war iddaren am tamja niɣ lgambri, ggin řḥess. Mařa war ggin řfarz jar ijj n řḥess d umas, mammec ɣa ssnen inni ittesřan min ttiraren s tamja niɣ s lharpa?  
\v 8 Iwa, mařa asuḍi deg uyicc ittegg řḥess war iṣfi, wi ɣa isswejden \add xenni\add* i umenɣi?  
\v 9 Ammu ɛawed kenniw, mařa tessiwiřem awařen s ijj n yiřes \add nneɣni\add*, maca war ten tfessarem, mammec ɣa fehmen min teqqarem? Ad tessiwřem xenni am wenni issawařen di řeɛwin.  
\v 10 Aqa din wi issnen mecḥař n iřsawen di ddunect uca uřa d ijjen zzaysen war iǧi břa řḥess \add nnes\add*.  
\v 11 Xenni mařa war ssineɣ řaǧaɣ n řḥess, ad iřiɣ necc d ijj n ubarrani i wenni issawařen, d wenni issawařen ad yiři d abarrani i necc.   
\m
\v 12 Ammu ɛawed kenniw, umi tenjebdem ɣar tewhibin n Arruḥ, arzum ad tfeyyḍem di ṭṭweɛ n řebni n tmesmunt.   
\m
\v 13 Wenni issawařen s ca n iřes \add nneɣni\add*, ad iẓẓaǧ ḥima izemmar i ufessar nnes.  
\v 14 Minzi mařa necc ẓẓuǧeɣ s ca n yiřes \add nneɣni\add*, arruḥ inu aqa iẓẓuǧ, maca řefhamet inu ad teqqim břa řɣiǧet.  
\v 15 Mammec i ɣa ggeɣ? Ad ẓẓaǧeɣ s arruḥ inu, maca ad ẓẓaǧeɣ ɛawed s řeɛqeř inu, ad ɣennjeɣ s arruḥ inu, maca ad ɣennjeɣ ɛawed s řeɛqeř inu. \x ◘ \xo 14:15 \xt Afa. 5:19; Kul. 3:16. \x*  
\v 16 Mammec nneɣni, mařa tbarkem s Arruḥ, izemmar ḥed i din iqqimen am war ifhim, ad yini ‘Amin!’ i tẓaǧit n uqadi nnec, minzi netta war issin min teqqared.  
\v 17 Minzi waxxa cek tbarked mliḥ, maca wenni d ac yudsen war ittwabenni ca \add zi man aya\add*.  
\v 18 Necc ttqadiɣ AREBBI aqa ssawařeɣ s iřsawen ktar zzaywem marra,  
\v 19 maca di tmesmunt aqa meɛlik ufiɣ ad iniɣ xemsa n wawařen s řeɛqeř inu, ḥima ad ssřemdeɣ ɛawed inneɣni, x ɛecra-ařaf n wawařen s yijj n yiřes \add nneɣni\add*.   
\m
\v 20 \add A\add* aytma inu, war ttiřim d tarwa deg ixarriṣen nwem, maca iřim d iseyman di tuɛeffna, u iřim tiwḍem di řefhamet. \x ◘ \xo 14:20 \xt Mt. 18:3; 19:14; Afa. 4:14; 1 Bṭ. 2:1, 2. \x*  
\v 21 Aqa tura di Ccariɛa:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ad ssiwřeɣ i řgens-a\qt*  
\m \qt s ijj n řhard n řbarrani\qt*  
\m \qt u s ijj n yiřes nneɣni.\qt*  
\m \qt Waxxa ammu war d ayi ttesřin ca,\qt*  
\m \qt iqqar SIDI.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 14:21 \xt Aɛwd. 28:49; Ica. 28:11-12. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 22 Ammu xenni iřsawen d řeɛřamet, war iǧi i yinni yumnen, maca i yinni war yuminen ca, maca awař i ittwanabben zzayes war iǧi i yinni war yuminen, maca i yinni yumnen.   
\m
\v 23 Mařa marra tamesmunt tessmun u marra tuɣa ssawařen s iřsawen, uca \add xenni\add* udfen inni ijehřen niɣ inni war yuminen, ma nitni war qqaren belli aqa \add iwdan-a\add* ttxeřfen?  
\v 24 Maca mařa marra tnebbam uca yudef-dd ḥed war yumin niɣ ḥed ijheř, xenni wanita ad ittwasseqneɛ zi marra kenniw uca ad ittwawebbex zzaywem marra,  
\v 25 uca min innufaren deg wuř nnes ad ittwaɛarra. Netta ad yaḍar s wudem nnes, ad isjed i AREBBI, ad yini: “Aqa s tidett AREBBI aqa-t jar awem!”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aɛbad n tmesmunt s usettef u di řehna  
\m
\v 26 S uyenni ad awem iniɣ, \add a\add* aytma inu, mařa tmunem, ejj kuř ijjen zzaywem wenni ɣar iǧa ijj n uzehhid \add niɣ\add* ict n tɣuri \add niɣ\add* ijj n usargeb \add niɣ\add* ijj n yiřes \add niɣ\add* ijj n ufessar ad zzayes dd-inṭeq. Ejj ad yiři marra i řebni.  
\v 27 Mařa din ḥed issiweř s yijj n iřes \add nneɣni\add*, \add ejj i-ten\add* ad ssiwřen s tnayen niɣ s waṭṭas s třata yidsen, uca kuř ijjen \add zzaysen\add* s nnubet nnes, u ejj ijj ad t ifessar.  
\v 28 Maca mařa war din iǧi wi izemmaren ad ifessar, ad isqar netta di tmesmunt, ad issiweř i yixef nnes u i AREBBI.   
\m
\v 29 Jjem ad ssiwřen tnayen niɣ třata n inabiyyen, uca inneɣni ad ḥekmen.  
\v 30 Maca mařa ittwassargeb ca i ḥed am iqqim dinni, ejj xenni ad issusem wenni issawařen d amezwaru,  
\v 31 Minzi tzemmarem ad tnebbam marra ijjen awarni wenneɣni, ḥima marra ad řemden uca ad daysen ittwagg wuř marra.  
\v 32 Maɣar arruḥ n inabiyyen, aqa-t immars sadu inabiyyen,  
\v 33 minzi AREBBI war iǧi d AREBBI n uxarweḍ, maca n řehna, ammu \add i yeǧa\add* di marra timesmunin n imqeddasen.   
\m
\v 34 Tusa-dd x temɣarin nwem ad ssusment di tmesmunin, minzi war d asent ismiḥ ad ssiwřent, maca icuwwar asent ad iřint ttwaḍɛent am mammec teqqar ɛawed Ccariɛa. \x ◘ \xo 14:34 \xt Amz. 3:16; Afa. 5:22; Kul. 3:18; 1 Tim. 2:12; Tit. 2:5; 1 Bṭ. 3:1. \x*  
\v 35 Uca mařa xsent ad řemdent ca, ad sseqsant iryazen nsent di taddart nsen, minzi aqa-tt d řefḍiḥet i temɣarin ad ssiwřent di tmesmunt.  
\v 36 Ma zeɛma iffeɣ-dd zzaywem awař n AREBBI? Niɣ yiweḍ-dd ɣarwem waha?   
\b  
\m
\v 37 Mařa ḥed ittɣiř as d anabi niɣ d bnadem arruḥani, ejj i-t ad iɛqeř mliḥ belli min d awem ttariɣ, aqa atent d tiweṣṣa n Siditneɣ.  
\v 38 Maca mařa \add ixs\add* ḥed ad iqqim ijheř, ejj i-t ad ijheř.  
\v 39 Ammu xenni, \add a\add* aytma inu, njebdem ḥima ad tnebbam, war mennɛem ca awař s iřsawen \add inneɣni\add*.  
\v 40 Ad imsar marra s ladab u s usettef.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Tanukra n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ  
\m
\v 1 \add A\add* aytma inu, ad awem ssargbeɣ x L’Injil wenni d awem barrḥeɣ, d wenni tqebřem u d wenni di tbeddem \add nican\add*,  
\v 2 i zi tᵉṭṭfem Tudart, s Wawař i d awem barrḥeɣ, mařa \add xas\add* tɛeqřem ɛad. Mammec nneɣni, zeɛma tumnem amenni waha. \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Rum. 1:16; 1 Kur. 1:21. \x*  
\v 3 Minzi zeg umezwar sseɛduɣ awem-dd min tuɣa ṭṭfeɣ s yixef inu, aqa Lmasiḥ immut x ddnub nneɣ ɛlaḥsab min yuran, \x ◘ \xo 15:3 \xt Ica. 53:7; Dan. 9:24, 26; 1 Kur. 5:7; 1 Bṭ. 2:24. \x*  
\v 4 aqa ittwanḍeř uca ittwassnekkar-dd deg wass wiss třata ɛlaḥsab min yuran. \x ◘ \xo 15:4 \xt Izhd. 16:10; Ica. 53:8, 9; Yun. 2:1; Mt. 12:40. \x*  
\v 5 Netta iḍhar-dd ɣar Kifa, xenni ɣar tenɛac \add n imeḥḍaren\add*. \x ◘ \xo 15:5 \xt Lk. 24:34; Yḥ. 20:19; Řex. 10:41. \x*  
\v 6 Awarni as iban-dd i tiwwa n xemsa-mya n wawmaten deg umur d ijjen, aṭṭas zzaysen ddaren \add ɛad\add* ař i řexxu, maca inneɣni aqa ṭṭṣen \add iḍeṣ n řmewt\add*.  
\v 7 Awarni as iḍhar-dd i Yaɛqub, xenni i marra rrusul.   
\m
\v 8 Am ɣar uneggar n marra, iḍhar ayi-dd ɛawed am i yijj n umexřuq dd-izwaren i řweqt nnes. \x ◘ \xo 15:8 \xt Řex. 9:3, 17; 23:11; 1 Kur. 9:1; 2 Kur. 12:2. \x*  
\v 9 Minzi necc ǧiɣ d amaẓuẓ qaɛ zi rrusul, war sdihijeɣ ad ayi řaɣan rrasul, minzi necc tuɣa darrceɣ x tmesmunt n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 15:9 \xt Afa. 3:8; Řex. 8:3; 9:1; 22:4; 26:9; Gal. 1:13; 1 Tim. 1:13. \x*  
\v 10 Maca s arḍa n AREBBI i ǧiɣ min ǧiɣ uca arḍa nnes i dayi iǧan war iǧi baṭeř, minzi xedmeɣ mahu qaɛ xasen marra, \add maca\add* war iǧi d necc, maca arḍa n AREBBI nni iǧan akidi. \x ◘ \xo 15:10 \xt 2 Kur. 11:23; 12:11. \x*  
\v 11 Xenni ma d necc niɣ d nitni, ammu i nettbarreḥ, ammu i tumnem.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tanukra n imettinen  
\m
\v 12 Maca mařa ittwabarreḥ s Lmasiḥ wenni dd-ittwassnekkaren zi taddart n imettinen, mammec xenni zemmaren ca jar awem ad inin belli war din bu Tudart i imettinen?  
\v 13 Minzi mařa war din bu Tudart i imettinen, uřa d Lmasiḥ war dd-ittwassnekkar ca,  
\v 14 uca mařa Lmasiḥ war dd-ittwassnekkar, xenni baṭeř i teǧa tbarreḥt nneɣ, baṭeř i yeǧa \add xenni\add* l’iman nwem.  
\v 15 Xenni neccin nban ɛawed d řechud issxarriqen n AREBBI, minzi neched x AREBBI belli aqa issnekkar-dd Lmasiḥ, waxxa Netta war i-t-i-dd-issnekkar ca.  
\v 16 Minzi mařa imettinen war dd-ttᵉtwasnekkaren ca, aqa Lmasiḥ war dd-ittwassnekkar ɛawed.  
\v 17 U mařa Lmasiḥ war dd-ittwassnekkar ca, aqa l’iman nwem ixwa, u aqa kenniw ɛad di ddnub nwem,  
\v 18 uca ttwahellken uřa d inni ittᵉṭṭṣen di Lmasiḥ \add awarni řami mmuten\add*.  
\v 19 Mařa tuɣa nessitim di Lmasiḥ di tudart-a waha, aqa aneɣ qaɛ d imcumen n marra iwdan.   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Maca řexxu umi dd-ittwassnekkar Lmasiḥ zi taddart n imettinen, aqa idweř Netta d Amenzu n yinni iṭṭṣen \add deg wenḍeř\add*. \x ◘ \xo 15:20 \xt Kul. 1:18; 1 Bṭ. 1:3; Asa. 1:5. \x*  
\v 21 U am mammec dd-tusa řmewt zeg ijj n bnadem, ammu uřa d tanukra n imettinen teǧa zeg ijj n Bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 15:21 \xt Amz. 2:17; 3:6; Rum. 5:12, 18; 6:23. \x*  
\v 22 Minzi am iwdan marra ad mmten di Adam, ammu ɛawed i ɣa ddaren marra nitni ɛawed di Lmasiḥ.  
\v 23 Maca kuř ijj di nnubet nnes: Lmasiḥ tuɣa d Amenzu, xenni awarni as inni iǧan n Lmasiḥ ɣar twasit nnes.  
\v 24 Awarni man aya d aneggaru, xmi ɣa iwc tageldit i AREBBI, Babatneɣ, xmi ɣa issebḍeř marra řeḥkamet d marra ṣṣulṭa d marra jjehd.   
\m
\v 25 Maɣar Netta ad iḥkem am Ujeǧid ař d ɣa yegg marra řɛedyan nnes sadu iḍaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 15:25 \xt Izhd. 110:1; Řex. 2:34; Afa. 1:20; Kul. 3:1; Ɛbr. 1:13; 10:12. \x*  
\v 26 Řeɛdu aneggaru wenni i ɣa ittwabeḍřen, aqa-tt d řmewt.  
\v 27 Minzi aqa igga marra sadu iḍaren nnes. Maca xmi ittwanna: “Aqa marra timesřayn ttwaggent sadu Netta!”, aqa iban \add mliḥ\add* belli wenni d as iggin marra sadu Netta, aqa Netta simant nnes war iǧi sadu Netta. \x ◘ \xo 15:27 \xt Izhd. 8:7; Mt. 11:27; 28:18; Afa. 1:22; Ɛbr. 2:8. \x*  
\v 28 Uca řami d as ittwagg marra sadu i Netta, řexdenni Mmis \add n AREBBI\add* ɛawed ad ittwagg sadu i Wenni umi d as iggin marra sadu i Netta, ḥima ad yiři AREBBI d marra di min di mma.   
\m
\v 29 Niɣ, min ɣa ggen inni ittwassɣeḍṣen di ṭṭweɛ n imettinen mařa war dd-tᵉttwassnekkaren imettinen ɛemmarṣ? Maɣar mayemmi ɣa ttwassɣeḍṣen ɛad di ṭṭweɛ n imettinen?  
\v 30 U mayemmi neccin \add ɛad\add* di lxaṭar di kuř tsaɛɛet?  
\v 31 \add A\add* aytma, ttjaǧiɣ ɣar usemɣar nwem i iǧan ɣari di Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, aqa ttmettiɣ kuř ass.  
\v 32 U mammec, mařa ttwamenḍareɣ zzat i řewḥuc di Afasus x řeḥsab bnadem, man řefḍeř i ɣari, mařa imettinen war dd-ttwassnekkaren ca? Ejj aneɣ ad necc ad nsu, minzi tiwecca ad nemmet. \x ◘ \xo 15:32 \xt Ica. 22:13; 56:12. \x*  
\v 33 War ttɣeccim yixef nwem: řhard war iḥřin tjeyyaḥ nneyyet taṣebḥant.  
\v 34 Sfaqem uřawen nwem \add ɣar\add* tsegda, war xeṭṭim ca. Minzi ca \add zzaywem\add* war ɣarsen teǧi tussna n AREBBI. I řeḥya nwem qqareɣ tt.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Arrimet n tnukra war ifennin  
\m
\v 35 Ad inin ca zzaywem: “Mammec i dd ɣa ttwassnekkaren imettinen? S man arrimet i dd ɣa yasen?” \x ◘ \xo 15:35 \xt Ḥiz. 37:3. \x*  
\v 36 \add A\add* afɣuř, min tzarrɛed cek, war iddar mařa war immut \add qbeř\add*. \x ◘ \xo 15:36 \xt Yḥ. 12:24. \x*  
\v 37 Min tzarrɛed, war teǧi ca d arrimet nni i ɣa tiři, maca tzarrɛed taɛeqqact iɣeryen n yirden niɣ n imendi niɣ n ca n zzariɛet nneɣni.  
\v 38 Maca AREBBI iwca as arrimet am mammec ixs Netta, i kuř ddab n zzariɛet iwca as arrimet ɛlaḥsab ṭṭbiɛet n kuř icten zzaysent.   
\m
\v 39 War iǧi marra arrimet \add d arrimet\add* d ijj, maca tenni n iwdan immsebḍa x tenni n řmař, u tenni n ijḍaḍ wenneɣni n tenni n iseřman.   
\m
\v 40 Aqa din arrimat n ujenna d arrimat n temmurt, maca aɛuǧi n yinni n ujenna wenneɣni n yinni n temmurt.  
\v 41 Ijjen d aɛuǧi n tfuct, wenneɣni d aɛuǧi n uyur, u wenneɣni d aɛuǧi n itřan, uca aɛuǧi n ijj n itři iɛeddun x uɛuǧi n ijj n itři nneɣni.   
\m
\v 42 Ammu xenni i ɣa tiři Tudart i yinni mmuten. Aqa ttwazarrɛen nitni di min iɣeccen uca ttwassnekkaren-dd břa řɣecc. \x ◘ \xo 15:42 \xt Dan. 12:3; Mt. 13:43. \x*  
\v 43 Aqa ttwazarrɛen nitni di min war icniɛen, \add maca\add* ad dd-ttwassnekkaren deg uɛuǧi. Nitni ttwazarrɛen deg weḍɛaf, \add maca\add* ad dd-ttwassnekkaren di jjehd.  
\v 44 Aqa ttwazarrɛen nitni s ict n arrimet n ṭṭbiɛet uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-ittwassnekkar \add bnadem\add* s ict n arrimet tarruḥanit. Aqa din arrimet n ṭṭbiɛet, ammu aqa din uřa d arrimet n Arruḥ.   
\m
\v 45 Ammu i tura ɛawed: “Aryaz amezwaru Adam, \add idweř\add* d řeɛmar iddaren!”, Adam aneggaru idweř d Arruḥ i itticen Tudart. \x ◘ \xo 15:45 \xt Amz. 2:7. \x*  
\v 46 Maca min \add iǧan\add* zi Arruḥ war dd-yusi ca d amezwaru, maca min iǧan n ṭṭbiɛet, xenni awarni man aya min \add iǧan\add* zi Arruḥ.  
\v 47 Bnadem amezwaru ikka-dd zeg ucař n temmurt, Bnadem wiss tnayen d SIDI i dd-ikkin zeg ujenna.  
\v 48 Am mammec iǧa wenni zeg ucař, ammu i ǧan uřa d nitni zeg ucař, uca am mammec iǧa Wenni n ujenna, ammu i ǧan uřa d inni \add n ujenna\add*.  
\v 49 Uca am mammec narbu ṣṣifet n wenni ittwaggen zeg ucař, ammu xenni ad narbu ṣṣifet n Wenni iǧan zeg ujenna. \x ◘ \xo 15:49 \xt 2 Kur. 4:11. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 50 \add A\add* aytma inu, ddegga \add xseɣ\add* ad iniɣ: Aqa aysum d idammen war zemmaren ad warten Tageldit n ijenwan, uca min ifennan war iwarret min war ifennin. \x ◘ \xo 15:50 \xt Yḥ. 1:13. \x*  
\v 51 Xzarem, ad kenniw ssaregbeɣ x ijj n ssirr: aqa aneɣ war nettᵉṭṭeṣ ca marra \add s yiḍeṣ n řmewt\add*, maca neccin marra ad nettwabeddeř, \x ◘ \xo 15:51 \xt 1 Ts. 4:16. \x*  
\v 52 deɣya, deg wermac n wabřiwen, ɣar \bd řḥess n usuḍi aneggaru deg uyicc \+bdit n icarri\+bdit*\bd*: imettinen ad dd-ttwassnekkaren ɣar min war ifennin uca neccin ad nettwabeddeř. \x ◘ \xo 15:52 \xt Mt. 24:31; 1 Ts. 4:16. \x*  
\v 53 Minzi min ifennan ittxeṣṣa as ad yarḍ min war ifennin u min ɣa immuten ittxeṣṣa as ad yarḍ min war ittmettin.   
\m
\v 54 Uca xmi min ifennan ad yarḍ min war ifennin u min ɣa immuten \add ad yarḍ\add* min war ittmettin, řexdenni ad ikemmeř wawař i ittwarin:  
\b  
\m \qt “Řmewt aqa tᵉttwaṣarḍ deg řeɣřeb.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:54 \xt Ica. 25:8. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 55 \qt “\+tl A\+tl* řmewt, mani iǧa usennan nnem?\qt*  
\m \qt A řaxart, mani iǧa řeɣřeb nnem?”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:55 \xt Ḥuc. 13:14; Ɛbr. 2:14. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 56 Aqa asennan n řmewt d ddenb, uca jjehd n ddenb aqa-tt d Ccariɛa.  
\v 57 Maca aqadi i AREBBI, wenni d aneɣ iwcin řeɣřeb s Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 15:57 \xt 1 Yḥ. 5:5. \x*   
\m
\v 58 S uya, \add a\add* aytma iɛizzen, beddem nican u břa anhezzi, arnim řebda di řxedmet n SIDI s ufeyyeḍ, am tessnem belli řxedmet nwem war teǧi baṭeř di SIDI.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 Asmuni n ṣṣdaqi i imqeddasen di Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 Zi jjihet n wesmuni \add n ṣṣdaqi\add* i imqeddasen, ggem kenniw ɛawed am mammec ḍebbreɣ i-tt-i-dd di tmesmunin n Galaṭiya.  
\v 2 Kuř \add ass\add* amezwar n ssimana kuř ijjen zzaywem ad iḥuz ca n tesɣart di taddart nnes uca ad tt ixemmeř ɛlaḥsab mammec iwesseɛ, ḥima, xmi dd ɣa awḍeɣ, war ibeddi ɛad řexdenni wesmuni \add n ṣṣdaqi\add*. \x ◘ \xo 16:2 \xt Řex. 11:29; 2 Kur. 8:4; 9:1. \x*  
\v 3 Uca xmi dd ɣa awḍeɣ, ad ssekkeɣ inni i ɣa tfarzem kenniw ak-d tebrat, ḥima ad awyen tacrimet \add n ṣṣdaqi\add* nwem ɣar Urcalim.  
\v 4 Uca mařa tuɣa icuwwar ad raḥeɣ necc ɛawed \add dinni\add*, xenni ad kkaren ad raḥen akidi.   
\m
\v 5 Ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ xmi dd ɣa kkeɣ x Makiduniya. Minzi ad dd-kkeɣ x webrid n Makiduniya, \x ◘ \xo 16:5 \xt 2 Kur. 1:15. \x*  
\v 6 uca mařa izemmar ad qqimeɣ akidwem niɣ ad sseɛduɣ řmecta akidwem, ḥima xenni kenniw tzemmarem ad ayi tessqebbḍem mani ɣa raḥeɣ.  
\v 7 Minzi war xseɣ ad kenniw ẓareɣ řexxu am dd xawem i ɣa kkeɣ abrid waha, minzi ssitimeɣ ad qqimeɣ akidwem ca n řweqt, mařa ismeḥ Sidi inu.  
\v 8 Maca ad qqimeɣ ɛad di Afasus ař ass n Řɛid n Xemsin n Wussan.  
\v 9 Minzi aqa tennurzem ayi-dd tewwart tameqqrant, \add maca\add* aqa din ijj n ubarru n řɛedyan.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Taneggarut d useǧem  
\m
\v 10 Mařa yiweḍ-dd Timutiyu ɣarwem, ḥḍam maḥend izemmar ad din yiři jar awem břa tiggʷudi, minzi netta ittegg řxedmet n SIDI am necc.  
\v 11 S uya uřa d ijjen ad t isseḥqar, maca qebbḍem t di řehna, ḥima ad ɣari dd-yas, minzi necc ttrajiɣ t ak-d wawmaten.   
\m
\v 12 Zi jjihet n tawmat Apullus, \add a\add* awmaten inu, aqa zawgeɣ t aṭṭas, ḥima ad ɣarwem dd-yas ak-d wawmaten, maca netta tuɣa war iɛewweř ad dd-yas řexxu, maca ad dd-yas xmi d as i ɣa isarreḥ řweqt.   
\m
\v 13 Ḥḍam, beddem nican di l’iman, ḥezmem s teryast, iřim tmeḥḍem.   
\m
\v 14 Jjem marra min tᵉtteggem ad yiři s tayri.   
\m
\v 15 Ttzawgeɣ kenniw, \add a\add* aytma, zi jjihet n twacunt n Stifanus, maɣar tessnem aqa aten d \add ṣṣabet\add* tamezwarut n Axaya, u nitni ṭewwɛen ixef nsen i tsexxart di ṭṭweɛ n imqeddasen,  
\v 16 aqa ggem ixef nwem sadu ufus n yinni am nitni uca sadu kuř ijjen i ixeddmen akidneɣ u i d \add aneɣ\add* ittɛawanen.   
\m
\v 17 Aqa farḥeɣ s twasit n Stifanus d Furtunatus d Axayikus, minzi nitni kemmřen min d ayi ittxeṣṣan daywem,  
\v 18 s minzi nitni ssareyyḥen arruḥ inu d wenni nwem. Weqqarem \add iryazen\add* am yina.   
\b  
\m
\v 19 Marra timesmunin n Asiya ttseǧament-i-dd xawem s řehna.  
\m Akwila d Priskilla ak-d tmesmunt i iǧan di taddart nsen ttseǧamen-dd xawem s řehna aṭṭas di Siditneɣ.   
\m
\v 20 Ttseǧamen-dd xawem marra awmaten nneɣ s řehna.  
\m Ttseǧamem-dd x wayawya s řehna s usudem iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 16:20 \xt Rum. 16:16; 2 Kur. 13:12; 1 Ts. 5:26; 1 Bṭ. 5:14. \x*   
\m
\v 21 Ijj n sřam i ttariɣ s ufus inu, zi Bulus.   
\b  
\m
\v 22 Mařa ḥed war ittexs Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, ad yiři d amenɛuř. Siditneɣ aqa yusa-dd! \f ◼ \fr 16:22 \ft \+fk Maran-ata\ft  - awařen-a xsen ad inin: ‘A Siditneɣ, as-dd’ niɣ ‘Siditneɣ aqa yusa-dd!’\f*  
\v 23 Arḍa n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ad yiři akidwem.  
\v 24 Tayri inu aqa-tt akidwem marra di Lmasiḥ Yasuɛ. Amin.   